Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.79,0:00:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸\NBaba...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.04,0:00:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事 兒子\NYes, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.42,0:00:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我講個故事吧\NTell me a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.92,0:00:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼故事\NWhich one?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,關於家鄉的故事\NThe story of home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.59,0:00:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,數百萬年前\NMillions of years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.13,0:00:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,一塊振金隕石撞向地球\Na meteorite made of vibranium...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,振金是宇宙中最為堅硬的物質\Nthe strongest substance in the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.34,0:00:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,隕石最終落在了非洲大陸上..\Nstruck the continent of Africa...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.41,0:00:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,影響改變了周圍的植被\Naffecting the plant life around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.44,0:00:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,待到人類的時代來臨\NAnd when the time of man came...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,五個部落定居在此並稱此地為 瓦坎達\Nfive tribes settled on it and called it Wakanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.22,0:00:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這些部落之間經常爆發戰爭\NThe tribes lived in constant war with each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,直到一位戰鬥巫師\Nuntil a warrior shaman...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.29,0:00:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,見到了來自黑豹女神芭絲特的幻影\Nreceived a vision from the Panther Goddess Bast...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.39,0:00:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,引領他找到了心形草\Nwho led him to the Heart-Shaped Herb...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.16,0:00:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一種能賦予他超越人類的力量\Na plant that granted him
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,速度和直覺的植物\Nsuperhuman strength, speed and instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.17,0:00:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這名勇士成為了國王...\NThe warrior became king...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.84,0:01:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,也是第一代黑豹\Nand the first Black Panther...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.28,0:01:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦坎達的守護者\Nthe protector of Wakanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,四個部落都接受了國王的統治\NFour tribes agreed to live under the king's rule...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,只有賈巴裏部落孤居在雪嶺之間\Nbut the Jabari Tribe isolated themselves in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.19,0:01:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦坎達人民利用振金發展科技\NThe Wakandans used vibranium to develop technology...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,比全世界所有國家都先進\Nmore advanced than any other nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.86,0:01:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,然而隨著瓦坎達的崛起\NBut as Wakanda thrived...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.53,0:01:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,它周圍的世界卻陷入了更深的混亂\Nthe world around it descended further into chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.00,0:01:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,為了保證振金的安全\NTo keep vibranium safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.50,0:01:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦坎達人民決意要隱匿於世\Nthe Wakandans vowed to hide in plain sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.41,0:01:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不向外界展露\Nkeeping the truth of their power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他們真實的力量\Nfrom the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.01,0:01:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我們還在潛伏麼 爸爸\NAnd we still hide, Baba?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.88,0:01:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.78,0:01:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.53,0:01:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 運氣球  - 才不是運氣\N- Lucky shot! - That ain't lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.17,0:01:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 隨便吧  - 一邊去\NWhatever! Get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.73,0:01:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,注意\NCheck up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,過來 防守他\NPick your man up! He open.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.07,0:02:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼著\NWhere you at?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.24,0:02:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,快上  快上  快上\NLet's go, let's go, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.41,0:02:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,傳球 傳球\NPass! Pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我就知道 - 快點啊\N- Got you, E. - E, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.91,0:02:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,看我的\NWatch me get this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.71,0:02:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂姆·哈達威流  這招就該這麼叫\NTim Hardaway style. That's what I call it, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,來啊\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.62,0:02:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼樣\NWhat you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你拿我沒轍\NYou ain't got nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.69,0:02:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,聽著 我們只要保證快進快出\NHey, look, if we get in and out quick,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就沒什麼好擔心的\Nwon't be no worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.79,0:02:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你開車從西邊過來\NYou in the van, come in through from the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.02,0:02:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,轉到街角處\NCome around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,就停在這\N- Land right here. - Mmm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟雙胞胎把車停在這\NMe and the twins are pulling up right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這車就不要了 明白嗎 我們從這兒…\NWe're leaving this car behind, okay? We come this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,把槍收起來\NHide the straps.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是警察嗎\NYo, is it the Feds?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,兩個長得和格蕾絲·瓊斯一樣的妞\NIt's these two Grace Jones-looking chicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,還帶著矛\NThey're holding spears.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.63,0:03:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,開門\NOpen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你確定？\NYou serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,她們下次就不是敲門了\NThey won't knock again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.66,0:03:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你是誰\NWho are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,恩喬布王子  阿祖裏之子\NPrince N'Jobu, son of Azzuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,向我證明你是我們的一員\NProve to me you are one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,陛下\NMy King.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,退下\NLeave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這是詹姆斯 我以生命擔保他值得信任 他可以留下\NThis is James. I trust him with my life. He stays...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,只要您允許的話  特查卡國王\Nwith your permission, King T'Chaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,如你所願\NAs you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.56,0:03:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,起來吧\NAt ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,過來  兄弟\NCome, baby brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.24,0:04:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看看你過得怎樣\NLet me see how you are holding up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,看你體格很棒嘛\NYou look strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,女神保佑 我很健康\NGlory to Bast, I am in good health.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,家裏怎麼樣？\NHow is home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不怎麼樣\NNot so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟\NBaby brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我們家鄉遭到了襲擊\NThere has been an attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.66,0:04:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這個人...\NThis man...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,叫尤利西斯·克勞...\NUlysses Klaue...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,偷了我們0.25噸的振金\Nstole a quarter ton of vibranium from us...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,為了逃跑 他還在邊境地區引爆了炸彈\Nand triggered a bomb at the border to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我們死傷慘重\NMany lives were lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.71,0:04:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他知道我們藏置振金的地點...\NHe knew where we hid the vibranium...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,也知道如何有效發動襲擊\Nand how to strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他有內應\NHe had someone on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:04:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那你來這裏做什麼？\NWhy are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:05:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我想讓你看著我的眼睛\NBecause I want you to look me in the eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我你為什麼要背叛瓦坎達\Nand tell me why you betrayed Wakanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有背叛祖國\NI did no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴他你是誰\NTell him who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,巴杜之子 祖瑞\NZuri, son of Badu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯 詹姆斯 你騙了我？\NJames. James, you lied to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,放開他\NLeave him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直都是瓦坎達人的臥底？\NYou were Wakandan this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你背叛了瓦坎達\NYou betrayed Wakanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼可以欺騙我？\NHow could you lie to me like...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,住手\NStand down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你以為我們只派了你一個間諜到這裏嗎？\NDid you think that you were the only spy we sent here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,恩喬布王子\NPrince N'Jobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我命令你即刻回國...\Nyou will return home at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你將會面對議會的質詢\Nwhere you will face the Council...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,並向他們坦白你的罪行\Nand inform them of your crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,開球吧\NCheck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.35,0:06:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,防好你的人 防好你的人\NGuard your man, guard your man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,非洲小國瓦坎達正舉行全國哀悼\NThe tiny nation of Wakanda
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,逝世的特查卡國王\Nis mourning the death of its monarch, King T'Chaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,一周前 這位深受愛戴的統治者\NThe beloved ruler was one of many confirmed dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,在聯合國總部\Nafter a terrorist attack
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,的恐怖襲擊中喪生\Nat the United Nations a week ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他是眾多遇難者中的一位\NThe suspect has since been apprehended.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,嫌疑人現已被逮捕\NThough it remains one of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.69,0:07:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,即使瓦坎達是世界上最窮的國家之一\Nthe poorest countries in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,國內山巒起伏\Nfortified by mountain ranges...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,雨林密佈\Nand an impenetrable rainforest...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但該國從未參與過國際貿易\NWakanda does not engage
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,也從未接受過國際援助\Nin international trade or accept aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,繼承該國王位的人\NThe succession of the throne...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,會是前國王\Nis expected to fall to the oldest
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.47,0:07:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,的長子\Nof the king's two children...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是特查拉王子\NPrince T'Challa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,王子殿下...\NMy Prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就要到達他們上空了\Ncoming up on them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的 奧科燁 我自己能解決\NNo need, Okoye. I can handle this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我會盡快把娜奇雅救出來\NI will get Nakia out as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你見到她時 不要愣住就好\NJust don't freeze when you see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼？\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不會愣\NI never freeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,發生什麼了？\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.04,0:08:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,發動機壞了 不能啟動了\NIt's the car. It lost power. It won't start.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這車開不動了\NThe car no start.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼情況？\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,引擎壞了\NThe engine failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的也是\NOurs, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉 這是什麼？\NWhat is it, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,防禦陣型\NDefense positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,防禦陣型\NDefense positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,有人攻擊我們嗎？\NAre we under attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,防禦陣型\NDefense positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,恩喬 到那邊去\NGet around to the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,防禦陣型\NDefense positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 防禦陣型\NHey. Defense positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不要耍花招\NNo games.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你們看到了什麼？\NWhat do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,來了 來了\NCome in. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那邊  - 注意後方\NOver there! Look back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:10:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,當心\NWatch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,特查拉 不要\NT'Challa, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他還是個孩子\NThis one's just a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他也是被拐騙了\NHe got kidnapped as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.33,0:10:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,娜奇雅\NNakia...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.87,0:10:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我\NI...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.31,0:10:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我想..  - 嘿\N- I wanted... - Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她在我手裏 - 不許動 否則我就開槍了\NI have her! Don't move! I will shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我會馬上開槍的\NI will shoot her right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你還是愣住了\NYou froze.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\NAh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼來這？ 你壞了我的任務\NWhy are you here? You've ruined my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我父親去世了 娜奇雅\NMy father is dead, Nakia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,明天我將加冕為王\NI will be crowned king tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你明天能到場\NAnd I wish for you to be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你們自己回家吧\NCarry yourselves home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,帶上這個男孩 把他送回他的族人身邊\NAnd take the boy. Get him to his people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你\NThank you oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的事你們不許對任何人說\NYou will speak nothing of this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,娜奇雅姐姐\NSister Nakia...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.04,0:12:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,王子殿下\NMy Prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我們到家了\Nwe are home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,看多少次都不會膩\NThis never gets old.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:13:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,母后\NQueen Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,公主\NPrincess...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,請您節哀順變\NMy comfort for your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,0:14:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 娜奇雅\NThank you, Nakia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你能回來真是太好了\NIt is so good to have you back with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.15,0:14:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,帶她去河畔\NTake her to the River Province
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,為典禮做準備\Nto prepare her for the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是 將軍\NYes, General.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他是不是愣住了？\NDid he freeze?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,像被車燈嚇住的羚羊一樣\NLike an antelope in headlights.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你說完了嗎？\NAre you finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到我妹妹在大典日子前\NSo surprised my little sister came
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,親自來接我\Nto see me off before our big day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你想得美\NYou wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.65,0:14:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我是為了脈衝珠來的 我要給珠子做個升級\NI'm here for the EMP beads. I've developed an update.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,升級？不了吧 珠子挺好使的\NUpdate? No. It worked perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你還要我教你多少次？\NHow many times do I have to teach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不能因為一件工具目前能正常使用\NJust because something works
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,就覺得它不需要得到改進\Ndoesn't mean that it cannot be improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.39,0:14:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你在教我？ 你知道什麼？\NYou are teaching me? What do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.69,0:14:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,知道的比你多\NMore than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.96,0:14:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒要看看你的儀式禮服\NI can't wait to see what kind of update you make...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,能升級成什麼樣\Nto your ceremonial outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,舒莉\NShuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.97,0:15:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 媽媽\NSorry, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.97,0:15:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,今天你感覺如何？ 媽媽\NHow are you feeling today, Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,驕傲\NProud.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你父親將永遠記得這一天\NYour father and I would talk about this day all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.02,0:15:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他與我們同在...\NHe is with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,現在該你繼位稱王了\Nand it is your time to be king.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好\NGood morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,需要幫助嗎？\NHow can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.51,0:15:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 就隨便看看這些工藝品\NI was just checking out these artifacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他們告訴我你是這方面的專家\NThey tell me you're the expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以這麼說\NAh. You could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,它們很漂亮\NThey're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這是從哪兒來的？\NWhere's this one from?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,波波阿善提部落\NThe Bobo Ashanti tribe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是現在的加納\Npresent day Ghana...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,十九世紀的產物\N19th century.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎？\NFor real?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼這個呢？\NWhat about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這個來自貝寧的埃多族\NThat one's from the Edo people of Benin...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,十六世紀的\N16th century.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那你再和我說說這個\NNow, tell me about this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.35,0:16:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,也是來自貝寧 七世紀的產物\NAlso from Benin, seventh century.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我想 應該是富拉部落\NFula tribe, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.49,0:16:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不對\NNah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼？\NI beg your pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,表面上看來 它是被英國士兵從貝寧掠走的\NIt was taken by British soldiers in Benin
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,其實它來自瓦坎達\Nbut it's from Wakanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.99,0:16:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,它是用振金製成的\NAnd it's made out of vibranium.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不用多說了\NDon't trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,這個東西我從你這收了\NI'mma take it off your hands for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這些東西是不出售的\NThese items aren't for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你認為你的祖先是怎麼得到這些東西的呢？\NHow do you think your ancestors got these?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.11,0:16:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得他們是用合理的價錢買下來的？\NYou think they paid a fair price?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,還是直接奪走了它 就像他們奪走其它所有東西那樣？\NOr did they take it, like they took everything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 我必須...\NSir, I'm going to have to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.11,0:16:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,請你離開這裏了\Nask you to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,從我一進來\NYou got all this security in here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你就已經讓所有安保人員盯著我了\Nwatching me ever since I walked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但你忘了檢查\NBut you ain't checking for
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.35,0:16:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己吃進肚子裏的東西\Nwhat you put in your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 夥計 走吧\NAll right, mate. Let's have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.92,0:16:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,快點 夥計 別磨蹭了\NCome on, mate. Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:17:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得她好像不大對勁\NI think she might not be feeling too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 快找人幫忙 這裏\NSomebody get some help! Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,快叫醫生 嘿 誰快來幫忙一下\NCall a doctor, please! Please, somebody, come help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏需要緊急救護\NMedical emergency right away
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,西非展區 請馬上過來\Nin the West African Exhibit, please, right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.47,0:17:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,當心\NLook out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,大家請後退 配合一下 謝謝\NStep back, please. Step back. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,醫生來了 醫生來了\NComing through over there. Medics coming through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.87,0:17:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我去休息一下\NI'm gonna take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,請為這位女士讓讓路\NLet's give the lady some space, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,請退後 先生們\NStep back, please, gents.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,請退後\NStep back, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 過來\NHey, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.26,0:17:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,過來 過來 別害怕\NCome here. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以走了 但不要告訴任何人 好嗎？\NYou can go, but just don't tell anyone, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,老兄 你為什麼不直接在這裏開槍呢？\NBro, why you ain't just shoot him right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,因為犯罪現場\NBecause it's better to leave
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,越分散越好\Nthe crime scene more spread out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,讓這案子看起來像是外行人做的\NMakes us look like amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那現在呢 我們來看看\NNow then, let's see if you know
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.93,0:18:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是真的懂行\Nwhat you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這只是開胃菜\NThat's just a taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你發財了 小子\NYou're gonna be a rich boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那你最好把它快點賣掉\NYou better sell that quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,已經賣出去了\NIt's already sold!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你有什麼意圖\NWhatever you try,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦坎達人可能會出現\Nthe Wakandans'll probably show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那今天我可要爽了\NThat'll make my day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以一石二鳥\NI can kill two birds with one stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是想跟我說那也是振金吧？\NYou're not telling me that's vibranium, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 我只是在感受這個面具\NNah, I'm just feeling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,前進\NOnward!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,前進\NOnward!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我 祖瑞\NI, Zuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:20:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,巴杜之子..\Nson of Badu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.37,0:20:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,向各位介紹\Ngive to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.20,0:21:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,特查拉王子\NPrince T'Challa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,黑豹\Nthe Black Panther!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.22,0:21:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,王子殿下\NThe prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.78,0:21:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,現將黑豹之力\Nwill now have the strength of the Black Panther...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.82,0:21:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,移除\Nstripped away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.55,0:21:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,願祖上榮光永存\NPraise the ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,願祖上榮光永存\NPraise the ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.43,0:21:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,在儀式戰鬥中\NVictory in ritual combat...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.53,0:22:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,勝利來自另一方的投降或者死亡\Ncomes by yield or death.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.30,0:22:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,如果哪個部落有意派出勇士出戰\NIf any tribe wishes to put forth a warrior...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.07,0:22:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那我現在就向他指明\NI now offer...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.48,0:22:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,通向王位之路\Na path to the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.28,0:22:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,商人部落今天不參加王位挑戰\NThe Merchant Tribe will not challenge today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.75,0:22:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,邊疆部落今天不參加王位挑戰\NThe Border Tribe will not challenge today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.63,0:22:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,河流部落今天不參加王位挑戰\NThe River Tribe will not challenge today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.83,0:22:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,山礦部落今天不參加王位挑戰\NThe Mining Tribe will not challenge today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,還有哪位具有皇族血統的人\NIs there any member of a royal blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.54,0:22:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,想參加王位挑戰的嗎？\Nwho wishes to challenge for the throne?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,這個緊身內衣實在是太不舒服了\NThis corset is really uncomfortable...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.55,0:22:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,既然沒人挑戰 我們還是收拾收拾各回各家好吧？\Nso could we all just wrap it up and go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.46,0:22:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽\NMother!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.38,0:23:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他們是賈巴裏部落的？ - 是的\N- Are they Jabari? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.39,0:23:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,姆巴庫 你來這幹什麼？\NM'Baku, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是王位挑戰日\NIt's challenge day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.47,0:23:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我們從深山裏觀察你們\NWe have watched...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.84,0:23:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,聆聽你們\Nand listened from the mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.41,0:23:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你們這樣子 我們感到厭惡\NWe have watched with disgust...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.51,0:23:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你們居然讓一個小毛孩子\Nas your technological advancements
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.42,0:23:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,來監管你們那些先進科技\Nhave been overseen by a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.19,0:24:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,她蔑視傳統\NWho scoffs at tradition!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.36,0:24:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,現在你們還要把王位\NAnd now you want to hand the nation
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.33,0:24:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,交給這個連父王\Nover to this prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.90,0:24:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,都保護不了的王子手上\Nwho could not keep his own father safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.91,0:24:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不是嗎？\NMmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.34,0:24:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我們可不接受\NWe will not have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.24,0:24:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 我們不接受\NI said, we will not have it, oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.45,0:24:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我 姆巴庫...\NI, M'Baku...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.42,0:24:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,賈巴裏部落的領袖\Nleader of the Jabari...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.39,0:24:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我接受你的挑戰 姆巴庫\NI accept your challenge, M'Baku.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.06,0:24:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,願哈姆曼的榮光永存\NGlory to Hanuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.85,0:24:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,賈巴裏人就位\NJabari!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.98,0:24:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,多拉米拉吉護衛隊\NDora Milaje!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.41,0:24:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,前進\NOnward!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.46,0:25:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,王位挑戰開始\NLet the challenge begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.71,0:25:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.58,0:25:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,站起來\NStand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.99,0:25:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,來啊\NCome!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.96,0:25:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,特查拉\NT'Challa!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.31,0:25:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,現在你的神在哪?\NWhere is your god now?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.25,0:26:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.60,0:26:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,沒力氣\NNo powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.90,0:26:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,沒爪子\NNo claws.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.60,0:26:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有特製戰服\NNo special suit, oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.37,0:26:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就是一個普通人 不適合領導我們\NJust a boy not fit to lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.54,0:26:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,給他看你是誰\NShow him who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.89,0:26:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我是特查拉王子\NI am Prince T'Challa...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.09,0:26:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,特查拉國王的兒子\Nson of King T'Chaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.69,0:26:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以做到的 特查拉\NYou can do this, T'Challa!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.24,0:27:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,打的好\NYes!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.88,0:27:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,加油\NCome on!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.81,0:27:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,投降吧 別逼我殺你\NYield! Don't make me kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.28,0:27:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我寧願死\NI would rather die!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.29,0:27:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,特查拉\NT'Challa!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.46,0:27:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,特查拉\NT'Challa!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.26,0:27:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,特查拉\NT'Challa!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.26,0:27:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,特查拉\NT'Challa!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.13,0:27:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,特查拉\NT'Challa!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.00,0:27:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你已帶著榮譽而戰\NYou have fought with honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.43,0:27:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,現在投降吧 你的子民需要你\NNow yield! Your people need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.24,0:27:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,特查拉\NT'Challa!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.57,0:27:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,特查拉\NT'Challa!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.64,0:27:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,投降 兄弟\NYield, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.11,0:27:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,特查拉\NT'Challa!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.64,0:27:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,特查拉\NT'Challa!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.51,0:27:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NYes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.57,0:27:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我向各位宣佈\NI now present to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.37,0:28:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,特查拉成功繼承王位\NKing T'Challa...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.41,0:28:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,黑豹\Nthe Black Panther.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.32,0:28:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,祖瑞\NZuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.35,0:28:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,國王陛下\NMy King.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.27,0:28:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦坎達萬歲\NWakanda forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.90,0:28:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦坎達萬歲\NWakanda forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.40,0:29:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,讓這個心形草\NAllow the Heart-Shaped Herb...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.07,0:29:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,恢復黑豹的力量\Nto restore the powers of the Black Panther...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.24,0:29:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,帶你前往先祖的世界\Nand take you to the Ancestral Plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.88,0:29:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,特查卡\NT'Chaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.25,0:29:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我們向您發起召喚\Nwe call on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.39,0:29:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,來這見您的兒子\NCome here to your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.02,0:29:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,願祖上榮光永存\NPraise the ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.19,0:31:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,父親\NFather.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.57,0:31:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我的兒子\NMy son.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.04,0:31:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.74,0:31:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,站起來\NStand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.71,0:31:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你是一個國王\NYou are a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.85,0:31:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？ 兒子\NWhat is wrong my son?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.27,0:31:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我還沒準備好\NI am not ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.44,0:31:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你這一生不是\NHave you not prepared
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.94,0:31:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,都在為當上國王做準備嗎?\Nto be king your whole life?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.57,0:31:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是一直在我身邊\NHave you not trained and studied,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.20,0:31:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,訓練 學習嗎？\Nbeen by my side?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.98,0:32:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我指的不是這個\NThat is not what I am talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.16,0:32:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我還是接受不了沒有你的日子\NI am not ready to be without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.53,0:32:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,一個男人如果沒有讓\NA man who has not prepared his children
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.70,0:32:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他的兒子坦然面對父親的離世\Nfor his own death...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.47,0:32:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那他就是一位失敗的父親\Nhas failed as a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.74,0:32:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我有讓你失望過嗎？\NHave I ever failed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.14,0:32:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,從來沒有\NNever.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.21,0:32:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,請告訴我如何才能守護好瓦坎達\NTell me how to best protect Wakanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.85,0:32:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望成為一個偉大的國王 爸爸\NI want to be a great king, Baba.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.82,0:32:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你一樣\NJust like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.89,0:32:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你會面臨很多困難\NYou're going to struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.96,0:32:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你要任用\NSo you'll need to surround yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.90,0:32:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,自己信任的人\Nwith people you trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.80,0:32:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你是一個好男人 同時也有著一顆善良的心\NYou're a good man with a good heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.07,0:32:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,對於一個好人來說 當國王很艱難\NAnd it's hard for a good man to be king.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.01,0:32:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,呼吸\NBreathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.68,0:33:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,特查拉 呼吸\NT'Challa, breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.88,0:33:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,呼吸\NBreathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.32,0:33:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他在那\NHe was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.32,0:33:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他就在那 我的父親\NHe was there. My father.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.47,0:33:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,只要一個\NJust one?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.15,0:33:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,回家吧 娜奇雅\NCome home, Nakia.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.15,0:33:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在家啊\NI'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.69,0:33:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,留下來\NStay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.59,0:33:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我來是對你表示支持 和悼念你的父親的\NI came to support you and to honor your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.53,0:33:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不能留下來\Nbut I can't stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.73,0:33:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,外面的世界需要我\NI found my calling out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.43,0:33:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我見過太多人對需要幫助的人視而不見\NI've seen too many in need just to turn a blind eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.07,0:33:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我留在這是不會快樂的\NI can't be happy here...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.47,0:33:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我心裏總會惦記著那些一無所有的人\Nknowing that there's people out there who have nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.61,0:34:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你希望瓦坎達做什麼呢？\NWhat would you have Wakanda do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.04,0:34:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,分享我們的科技\NShare what we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.84,0:34:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我們可以提供援助\NWe could provide aid...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.58,0:34:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,和技術支持\Nand access to technology
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.45,0:34:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,為那些需要的人提供庇護\Nand refuge to those who need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.12,0:34:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,其他國家也在做 我們可以做的更棒\NOther countries do it, we could do it better.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.05,0:34:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我們與這些國家是不同的 娜奇雅\NWe are not like these other countries, Nakia.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.46,0:34:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,如果世界瞭解了我們的真相\NIf the world found out what we truly are...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.19,0:34:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,知道我們所擁有的一切\Nwhat we possess...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.93,0:34:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我們將會失去原有的生活\Nwe could lose our way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.60,0:34:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦坎達足夠強大 幫助其他人的同時\NWakanda is strong enough to help others
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.10,0:34:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,也能夠保護自己\Nand protect ourselves at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.60,0:34:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不那麼固執己見 會是一個偉大的皇后\NIf you were not so stubborn, you would make a great queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.67,0:34:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,正因為固執 我才能成為一個偉大的皇后\NI would make a great queen because I am so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.38,0:34:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢 你看你已經承認了 - 如...如果我想當的話\N- Ah! See, you admit it! - If that's what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.15,0:34:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是他嗎？\NIs that him?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.96,0:34:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,女神保佑 他還在長大嗎\NGlory to Bast, man. Is he still growing?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.60,0:34:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,當然\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.26,0:34:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到娜奇雅回來了\NI see Nakia is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.87,0:34:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你們倆會復合嗎？\NYou guys going to work it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.47,0:35:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,特查拉\NT'Challa...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.14,0:35:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？\Nwhat's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.91,0:35:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,娜奇雅認為我們應該做更多的事\NNakia thinks we should be doing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.71,0:35:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,比如說？\NMore, like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.85,0:35:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,對外援助 難民項目\NForeign aid, refugee programs.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.19,0:35:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你讓難民涌入\NYou let the refugees in...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.59,0:35:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他們的麻煩也會跟著進來\Nthey bring their problems with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.69,0:35:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,之後瓦坎達就會變得像其他地方一樣\NAnd then Wakanda is like everywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.09,0:35:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,如果現在你要我和我的將士們一起\NNow if you said you wanted me and my men...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.66,0:35:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,走出國門 蕩盡世間不平事\Nto go out there and clean up the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.70,0:35:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也必定全力以赴\Nthen I'll be all for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.54,0:35:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但是就這麼向其他國家發動過戰爭\NBut waging war on other countries
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.77,0:35:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我們的行事風格\Nhas never been our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.04,0:35:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你的也響了？\NYou, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.18,0:35:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,天呀 我們有麻煩了\NBast! We're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.92,0:35:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,國王陛下\NMy King.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.95,0:35:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我的愛人\NMy love.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.45,0:35:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定猜不到我們在雷達裏發現了誰\NYou will never guess who just popped up on our radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.29,0:35:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,一件瓦坎達王國手工藝品 曾被誤認為是其他文明的手工製品\NA misidentified Wakandan artifact...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.26,0:36:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天被人從一家英國博物館盜走\Nwas stolen yesterday from a British museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.23,0:36:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我們得知尤利西斯·克勞\NWe have learned Ulysses Klaue...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.37,0:36:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,計劃把那件振金製品\Nplans to sell the vibranium to an American buyer...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.37,0:36:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,在韓國出售給一位美國買家\Nin South Korea...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.97,0:36:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,交易時間是明天晚上\Ntomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.88,0:36:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,近30年來 我們一直沒能抓到克勞\NKlaue has escaped our pursuits for almost 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.75,0:36:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有抓到他 或許是我父親最大的遺憾\NNot capturing him is, perhaps, my father's greatest regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.45,0:36:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望把克勞帶回來接受審判\NI wish to bring Klaue back here to stand trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.66,0:36:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦坎達王國現在需要的不是一個戰士\NWakanda does not need a warrior right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.89,0:36:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我們需要一個國王\NWe need a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.83,0:36:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我的父母在他的襲擊中喪生\NMy parents were killed when he attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.60,0:36:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我每天都在想著\NNot a day goes by when I do not think
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.53,0:36:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,克勞從我們這奪走的一切\Nabout what Klaue took from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.51,0:36:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他從我身上奪去的那些\NFrom me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.54,0:36:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼好的機會 怎能錯過\NIt's too great an opportunity to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.51,0:36:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,把我帶上\NTake me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.68,0:36:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我們並肩作戰一起把他拿下\NWe'll take him down together, side by side.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.81,0:36:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你在這保護邊疆\NI need you here protecting the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.18,0:36:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那我得問一句\NThen I ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.52,0:36:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你是當場殺了他呢\Nyou kill him where he stands...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.95,0:36:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,還是把他帶回到我們這呢？\Nor you bring him back to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.82,0:36:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你保證\NYou have my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.06,0:37:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我會把帶回來\NI will bring him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.53,0:37:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就這麼干\NWe will proceed with the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.81,0:37:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,國王陛下\NMy King!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.75,0:37:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣 別這樣\NStop it. Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.35,0:38:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經幫你往釜山提前送了一輛車過去\NI've already sent a car ahead to Busan for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.39,0:38:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你要帶誰和你一起去韓國？\NWho are you taking with you to Korea?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.82,0:38:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,奧科燁\NOkoye.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.46,0:38:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,還有娜奇雅\NAnd Nakia as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.06,0:38:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你確定帶前女友執行任務是個好主意？\NYou sure it's a good idea to take your ex on a mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.63,0:38:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.84,0:38:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我們會沒事的\NWe'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.90,0:38:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你要隨時待命 我們需要支援\NBesides, you'll be on call should we need backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.01,0:38:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了\NYes!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.27,0:38:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我給你看些好東西 哥哥\NI have great things to show you, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.71,0:38:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這是你到韓國用的通訊設備\NHere are your communication devices for Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.08,0:38:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,無限範圍\NUnlimited range,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.68,0:38:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,還裝備有音頻監控系統\Nalso equipped with audio surveillance system.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.82,0:38:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,看看這些\NCheck these out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.36,0:38:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,遠程控制的基莫由珠\NRemote access Kimoyo Beads.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.49,0:38:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,升級過的界面直接和我的沙盤相連\NUpdated to interface directly with my sand table.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.90,0:38:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\NAh.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.13,0:38:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這些是什麼？\NAnd what are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.33,0:38:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,真正的問題應該是 你穿的是什麼？！\NThe real question is what are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.40,0:38:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你要在我的實驗室裏露出腳趾？\NWhy do you have your toes out in my lab?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.91,0:38:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？你不喜歡我的皇家涼鞋？\NWhat, you don't like my royal sandals?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.04,0:38:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我上任第一天想走復古路線\NI wanted to go old school for my first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.21,0:38:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我估計長老們會喜歡你這裝束的\NI bet the Elders loved that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.35,0:38:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,穿上試試\NTry them on.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.42,0:39:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,全自動的\NFully automated.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.79,0:39:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,就像爸爸常看的美國老電影\NLike the old American movie Baba used to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.26,0:39:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NMmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.46,0:39:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我研製的鞋具有完美吸音特性\NAnd I made them completely sound absorbent.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.79,0:39:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,有意思\NInteresting.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.93,0:39:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,猜我怎麼叫它們\NGuess what I call them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.86,0:39:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,運動鞋\NSneakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.03,0:39:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你...\NBecause you...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.27,0:39:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,當我沒說\NNever mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.84,0:39:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想活捉克勞\NIf you're going to take on Klaue...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.24,0:39:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你就需要設計團隊提供給你的最尖端裝備\Nyou'll need the best the design group has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.91,0:39:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,看這第一件戰服\NExhibit A.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.94,0:39:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 這是我設計的 - 過時的技術\N- My design. - Old tech.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.71,0:39:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 很老嗎？ - 能湊合用 但還是太過時了\N- Old? - Functional, but old.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.25,0:39:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,「嘿 有人向我開槍\N"Hey, people are shooting at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.05,0:39:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 讓我先戴上頭盔」\N"Wait, let me put on my helmet."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.15,0:39:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了吧\NEnough.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.89,0:39:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,現在 瞧瞧這些\NNow, look at these.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.46,0:39:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜歡那件嗎？\NDo you like that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.96,0:39:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,很吸引人\NTempting.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.90,0:39:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但是金色太顯眼 不夠低調\NBut the idea is to not be noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.24,0:39:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我要這件\NThis one.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.28,0:40:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,現在讓戰服展示完整形態\NNow tell it to go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.28,0:40:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,哇哦\NOoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.19,0:40:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,整個戰服都集成在牙齒項鏈上\NThe entire suit sits within the teeth of the necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.72,0:40:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,打它一下\NStrike it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.53,0:40:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 打哪都行？ - 是的\N- Anywhere? - Mmm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.66,0:40:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪 別這麼用力\NNot that hard, genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.43,0:40:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你讓我打的 你又沒說用多大力度\NYou told me to strike it. You didn't say how hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.74,0:40:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我邀請你來我的實驗室\NI invite you to my lab,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.24,0:40:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你卻到處搞破壞嗎？\Nand you just kick things around?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.74,0:40:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 或許你該把它做的更牢固些\NWell, maybe you should make it a little stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.78,0:40:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\NHey.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.88,0:40:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下\NWait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.44,0:40:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,戰服內的納米機器人會吸收動能\NThe nanites absorb the kinetic energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.35,0:40:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,動能會被儲存於戰服內 便於戰服再次使用\Nand hold it in place for redistribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.02,0:40:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒\NVery nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.42,0:40:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你再打一下剛才的地方\NStrike it again in the same spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.89,0:40:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你在錄像？\NYou're recording?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.96,0:40:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,科研需要嘛\NFor research purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.10,0:40:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,刪除那段錄像\NDelete that footage.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.82,0:41:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊\NThis way.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.76,0:41:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,芭斯特女神的旨意 行動會很快結束\NBast willing, this will go quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.60,0:41:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,然後我好摘掉這該死的假髮\Nand I can get this ridiculous thing off my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.73,0:41:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好看的啊  你時不時前後甩甩頭髮\NIt looks nice. Just whip it back and forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.24,0:41:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？ 那太丟臉了\NWhat? It's a disgrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.82,0:41:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 索菲亞\NHello Sophia.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.78,0:41:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,很高興見到你\NGood to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.29,0:41:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這兩個人是誰？\NWho are these two?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.04,0:41:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是我肯尼亞那邊的朋友 超級有錢的 人很不錯\NMy friends from Kenya. Very deep pockets. They're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.04,0:41:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,惹麻煩的本事也很不錯吧...\NGood for trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.67,0:41:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,就跟你一樣\N...like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.10,0:42:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\NThank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.39,0:42:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,分開行動\NSpread out.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.76,0:42:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,買家可能已經到這了\NThe buyer is likely already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.15,0:42:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛外面的女人\NThe woman outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.52,0:42:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,她說的「麻煩」指的是什麼？\NWhat trouble was she referring to?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.92,0:42:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾與某些象牙商\NAh... I got into a disagreement
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.82,0:42:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,幹了一架\Nwith some ivory traders.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.82,0:42:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 惹了點小麻煩 - 這樣啊\N- Made a bit of a mess. - Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.93,0:43:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼今晚會有麻煩嗎？\NAnd will there be any trouble tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.33,0:43:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,富有的肯尼亞繼承人小姐\NMs. Kenyan Heiress?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.40,0:43:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這取決於...\NDepends...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.67,0:43:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我們完成任務的速度\Non how quickly we finish the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.97,0:43:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你們倆專注點好不好？\NCan we please focus?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.64,0:43:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.09,0:43:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊\NOver here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.30,0:43:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,來一杯威士忌\NOne whiskey, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.72,0:43:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,注意 有美國人\NEyes up. Americans.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.26,0:43:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我發現三個\NI count three.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.60,0:43:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是五個\NFive.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.84,0:43:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼能無視你身後\NHow could you miss Greased Lightning
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.37,0:43:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,的美國佬呢？\Nthere behind you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.90,0:43:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,六個\NSix.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.97,0:43:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我剛剛發現了一個就職於中央情報局的老朋友\NJust spotted an old friend who works for the CIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.61,0:43:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,事情變得有點複雜了\NIt just got a little more complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.52,0:43:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,羅斯探員\NAgent Ross.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.75,0:43:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,國王陛下\NYour Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.45,0:43:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你要和克勞做交易？\NYou are buying from Klaue.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.89,0:43:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我是代表美國政府\NWhat I'm doing or not doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.83,0:44:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,做什麼不做什麼\Non behalf of the U.S. government
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.43,0:44:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不用你操心\Nis none of your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.73,0:44:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你要做什麼...\NNow, whatever the hell you're up to...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.60,0:44:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,算幫我個忙 別來礙我的事\Ndo me a favor, stay out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.80,0:44:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是我把澤莫交給你的\NI gave you Zemo.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.37,0:44:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是也對你的秘密一直保持沉默嗎？\NDidn't I keep it under wraps...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.80,0:44:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你說的是你一個第三世界國家的國王\Nthat the king of a third world country
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.57,0:44:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,穿著防彈豹服在外面跑來跑去這個秘密 對吧？\Nruns around in a bulletproof cat suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.67,0:44:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,其實我們彼此彼此\NI'd say we were even.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.11,0:44:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你現在就應該離開這\NYou really need to leave, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.28,0:44:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我會把克勞一起帶走的\NKlaue is leaving out that door with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.81,0:44:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我可警告你了\NYou've been warned.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.45,0:44:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,骰子是三點\NThree, craps.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.19,0:44:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你贏了\NHey, you won!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.82,0:44:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道嗎？\NYou know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.19,0:44:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得我應該接手\NI think I'll just take these...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.53,0:44:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,把它們拿到我這邊來\Nbring them over here
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.16,0:44:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 代為保管 - 嗯\N- and hold on for safekeeping. - Mmm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.13,0:44:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 注意點 瓦坎達國王在這裏\NOkay, heads up. The king of Wakanda is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.54,0:44:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不能讓他帶走克勞\NHe cannot leave with Klaue.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.74,0:44:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.87,0:44:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,關於索科維亞事件中的振金\NVibranium from the attack on Sokovia
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.44,0:44:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,線索都指向了一個人\Nlinks back to a person...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.58,0:44:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然我不會明著承認\Nthat I'm not actually saying
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.74,0:44:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,可我是來跟這個人做交易的\NI'm here to make a deal with...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.88,0:44:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,而這筆交易是必須進行的\Nbut that deal will not be called off.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.52,0:44:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,所以當事情水落石出的時候\NWhen the dust settles,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.78,0:44:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我可以一起解決這件事\Nyou and me can work something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.55,0:45:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不是來這做交易的\NI'm not here to make a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.35,0:45:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,克勞 還帶了八個人來\NKlaue, plus eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.65,0:45:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,將軍那邊呢\NGeneral.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.79,0:45:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,已就位 保證我們的撤退路線安全\NIn position to secure our exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.82,0:45:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,振金呢？\NAnd the vibranium?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.92,0:45:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我還沒有看到\NI don't see it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.59,0:45:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我記得這裏是不許帶武器進來的吧\NI thought there were no weapons allowed in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.59,0:45:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,確實是這樣\NThere's not supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.53,0:45:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有些人不聽話\NSomebody did not get the memo.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.76,0:45:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對是帶著傢伙呢\NDefinitely armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.10,0:45:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,哼 你這些隨從還挺像樣的嘛\NWell, that is quite the entourage.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.14,0:45:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你這陣容是要出混音唱片嗎？\NYou got a mixtape coming out?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.40,0:45:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,對 沒錯 實話說我還真有一個\NOh, yeah. Yeah, actually, there is one.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.24,0:45:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想要 我把雲鏈接發給你\NI'll send you the SoundCloud link, if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.28,0:45:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 戴夫 你把那個鏈接...？\NHey, Dave, can you get the link to the tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.84,0:45:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託 我不想聽你的什麼音樂\NPlease, don't make me listen to your music.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.45,0:46:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思你帶的人太多了\NI just meant you got a lot of people with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.11,0:46:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你以為他們是為你準備的？\NYou think they're for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.22,0:46:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,別擔心\NDon't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.29,0:46:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,和你交易的只有我一個人\NI can do a deal with you all by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.46,0:46:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感謝\Nthank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.93,0:46:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,又來了六個人 這是個陷阱\NSix more. It's a setup.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.30,0:46:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,鑽石你帶來了吧？\NYou got the diamonds?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.50,0:46:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我想這些夠了吧\NOkay. That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.31,0:46:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我們得走了克勞 - 等會兒別動\N- We need to move on Klaue. - Stand down.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.04,0:46:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,要是來場槍戰我們可吃不消\NWe can't afford a shootout.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.11,0:46:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,振金的？\NVibranium?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.16,0:46:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 我本打算買逼格高點的手提箱的 不過...\NI was going to buy a fancy suitcase...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.39,0:46:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我還是想給我自己省點錢\Nbut I thought I'd save myself some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.56,0:46:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就現在 機不可失\NIt's now or never.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.30,0:46:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,別動\NStand down!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.06,0:46:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.47,0:46:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我被識破了\NI've been made.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.71,0:47:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦坎達人 是他們\NWakandans! They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.35,0:47:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快撤離此地  - 殺光他們\N- Get outta here! - Kill 'em all!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.92,0:47:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,帶上鑽石 快走\NDiamonds, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.09,0:48:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,殺人犯\NMurderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.49,0:48:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道嗎 你跟你老爸可真像\NYou know, you look just like your old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.57,0:48:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,鈔票滿天飛啊\NI made it rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.94,0:48:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我們撤吧 老闆\NLet's get out of here, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.38,0:48:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,太壯觀了 真刺激\NThat was awesome! That was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.61,0:48:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我們走 快走 快點啊\NLet's go! Go, go, go, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.95,0:48:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我們不管他了？ - 他會追上來的\N- Do we just leave him? - He'll catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.73,0:48:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,舒莉\NShuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.50,0:48:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 到我登場了\NYes!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.60,0:49:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,遠程駕駛系統已激活\NRemote driving system activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.84,0:49:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 車在路的哪邊？\NWait! Which side of the road is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.67,0:49:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天啊\NFor Bast's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.90,0:49:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 別管了 開就是了 - 好吧 冷靜\N- Just drive! - Okay, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.58,0:49:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,哇哦 出發嘍\NWhoo! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.29,0:49:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,來點音樂 這麼安靜幹嘛 參加葬禮嗎？\NPut some music on. What do you think this is, a funeral?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.16,0:49:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他在哪輛車上？\NWhich one is he in now?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.96,0:49:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 分頭走\NHey, split up!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.06,0:49:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他們想甩掉我們 - 我追右邊那輛\N- They're trying to lose us. - I'll take the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.97,0:49:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我們負責另外兩輛 我抄近道去追\NWe'll take the other two! I see a shortcut.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.72,0:49:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這我可過不去了\NWe're not going to make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.36,0:49:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續追\NKeep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.80,0:50:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 哥你厲害\NWhoo! Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.21,0:50:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 那是什麼鬼？\NHey, what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.61,0:50:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,別分心 你做的很好\NDon't worry about it. You're doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.36,0:50:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,還開槍呢\NGuns.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.69,0:50:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,攻擊手段真原始\NSo primitive!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.03,0:50:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那車是振金的 你這蠢貨\NIt's a vibranium car, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.96,0:50:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,子彈打不透\NThe bullets won't penetrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.27,0:50:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你要幹什麼？\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.63,0:50:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你開就是了\NJust drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.52,0:50:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 見鬼\N- Whoo! - Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.13,0:51:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 注意你的戰袍\NHey, look at your suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.00,0:51:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直在挨槍子\NYou've been taking bullets,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.17,0:51:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,戰袍會儲存動能的\Ncharging it up with kinetic energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.98,0:51:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,超過那輛車\NPull around the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.02,0:51:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他去哪兒了？\NWhere'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.69,0:51:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你真秀啊\NYou show-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.16,0:51:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,追上他了\NThere he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.70,0:51:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,抓緊\NHold tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.44,0:51:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 來點刺激的\NAll right. Let's have some fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.97,0:52:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,上車\NHop in.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.37,0:52:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,把矛放後備箱\NPut that spear in the trunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.04,0:52:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,加速 舒莉\NFaster, Shuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.28,0:52:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經開到最快了\NI'm going as fast as I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.52,0:52:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,右轉 右轉\NTake a right! Take a right!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.65,0:52:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 不 不 不\NNo, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.26,0:52:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥\NBrother!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.68,0:53:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,克勞\NKlaue!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.65,0:53:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得我們能忘的了嗎？\NDid you think we would forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.46,0:53:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,看著我 殺人犯\NLook at me, murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.37,0:53:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你從哪裏來搞到這個武器的？\NWhere did you get this weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.17,0:53:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你們這種野蠻人不配擁有它\NYou savages didn't deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.27,0:53:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 手下留情 國王 手下留情\NOh, mercy, King. Mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.78,0:53:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你的每一次呼吸都源自我的仁慈\NEvery breath you take is mercy from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.21,0:53:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,國王\NKing!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.08,0:53:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,全世界都看著呢\NThe world watches.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.15,0:53:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 幾位 我們撤 好吧？\NCome on. Guys. Let's go, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.09,0:53:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這就對了\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.67,0:54:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.58,0:54:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我能看到你 我能..我能看到你哦\NI can see you! I can. I can see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.59,0:54:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這動靜鬧得很大啊\NSo this is a big mess, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.49,0:54:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我們可以一個唱紅臉 一個唱白臉\NI figured we could go good cop, bad cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.79,0:54:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我先和他談 然後你們上\NI'll talk to him first, then you guys go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.38,0:54:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不能單獨和克勞談\NWe can't let him talk to Klaue alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.22,0:54:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他跟克勞談五分鐘 比在這裏鬧翻要好\NBetter to let him talk to Klaue alone for 5 minutes than to make a scene here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.28,0:54:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你審問完之後\NAfter your questioning,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.71,0:54:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我們會把他帶回瓦坎達\Nwe will take him back to Wakanda with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.78,0:54:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？ 不 聽著 我很欣賞你\NWhat? No. Look, I like you, a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.55,0:54:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但他現在是收押在我這 他哪也不能去\NBut he's in my custody now. He's not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.52,0:54:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,聽著 要不是我幫你們\NListen, I'm doing you guys a favor
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.32,0:54:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你們連這都進不來\Nby letting you even be in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.16,0:54:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他再碰你一次\NIf he touches you again,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.95,0:54:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我就把他釘到桌子上\NI'm going to impale him to this desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.53,0:54:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,她會說英語嗎？\NDoes she speak English?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.30,0:55:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她想說的時候才會說\NWhen she wants to.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.04,0:55:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我進去了\NI'm going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.14,0:55:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我結束之後 你們上\NWhen I'm done, you guys are up.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.41,0:55:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 特工羅斯  - 怎麼了？\N- Agent Ross. - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.65,0:55:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我很感謝你在釜山能幫我們\NI do appreciate your help in Busan.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.21,0:55:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你看見了吧\NYou see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.05,0:55:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這就叫外交\NIt's called diplomacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.28,0:55:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不客氣\NYou're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.49,0:55:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-  奧科燁 - 啊啊\NOkoye.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.82,0:55:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,客氣點\NPlay nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.03,0:55:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,美國人就這德性\NAmericans.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.94,0:55:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的不應該信瓦坎達人的話\NYou know, you really shouldn't trust the Wakandans.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.21,0:55:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,咱倆才是一個步調上的人\NI'm much more your speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.58,0:55:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,幹我這行的 從不相信任何人\NI don't trust anybody, not in this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.58,0:55:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但我感興趣的是那個手臂大炮\NBut what I am interested in is that arm cannon out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.31,0:55:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你從哪兒拿到的？\NWhere'd you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.65,0:55:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一個舊的採礦工具 我做了一些改裝\NIt's an old mining tool that I made some adjustments to.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.48,0:55:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我可以 送你一個 如果你喜歡的話\NBut I can get you one, if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.92,0:55:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要不你告訴我你供應商的名字\NWhy don't you give me the name of your supplier,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.06,0:55:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,然後我去問他們如何？\Nand I'll ask them.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.22,0:55:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他就在外面\NHe's right outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.72,0:55:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼不親自問問他呢？\NWhy don't you ask him yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.53,0:55:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？ 特查拉？\NWhat? T'Challa?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.06,0:56:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你是想跟我說你手臂上的武器來自瓦坎達？\NYou're telling me that weapon on your arm is from Wakanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.87,0:56:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,對了\NBingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.90,0:56:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你究竟對瓦坎達王國瞭解多少？\NWhat do you actually know about Wakanda?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.27,0:56:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,呃\NUm...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.61,0:56:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,牧羊人 紡織品 還有炫酷的衣服\NShepherds, textiles, cool outfits.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.81,0:56:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這都是表面的東西\NIt's all a front.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.74,0:56:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,探險家們找了幾個世紀\NExplorers searched for it for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.55,0:56:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,傳說中的黃金之城\NEl Dorado, the Golden City.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.05,0:56:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他們以為能在南美洲找到黃金之城\NThey thought they could find it in South America...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.65,0:56:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但是其實 黃金之城一直在非洲\Nbut it was in Africa the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.69,0:56:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這是一個科技鑄就的奇跡\NA technological marvel.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.66,0:56:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,它是以目前人類已知最珍貴的金屬\NAll because it was built on a mound
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.26,0:56:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,為基礎建立起來的\Nof the most valuable metal known to man.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.43,0:56:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他們叫它 天賜的禮物\NIsipho, they call it. The gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.17,0:56:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是振金\NVibranium.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.40,0:56:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,振金 地球上最堅硬的金屬\NVibranium, yeah, strongest metal on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.67,0:56:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這不僅僅是一種金屬\NIt's not just a metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.17,0:56:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他們還把它縫進衣服裏\NThey sew it into their clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.74,0:56:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,振金為他們的城市供能 強化了他們的科技水平\NIt powers their city, their tech...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.91,0:56:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,幫助他們生產出更強的武器\Ntheir weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.84,0:56:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,武器？\NWeapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.05,0:56:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.05,0:56:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我的手臂炮彈和他們的武器比起來跟玩具沒什麼兩樣\NMakes my arm cannon look like a leaf blower.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.58,0:56:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,故事編的挺好\NThat's a nice fairy tale,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.88,0:56:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但是瓦坎達是第三世界的國家\Nbut Wakanda is a third world country...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.95,0:56:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,而你偷了他們全部的振金\Nand you stole all their vibranium.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.66,0:56:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我偷走了...？\NI stole...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.39,0:57:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的？\NAll of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.03,0:57:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我只拿了一點點\NI took a tiny piece of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.63,0:57:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他們那裏的振金堆積如山\NThey have a mountain full of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.54,0:57:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他們已經挖掘了幾千年\NThey've been mining it for thousands of years...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.84,0:57:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,也不過是挖走了點皮毛而已\Nand they still haven't scratched the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.38,0:57:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我是唯一一個見過那景象\NI'm the only outsider who's seen it
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.41,0:57:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,還能活著回來的外來者\Nand got out of there alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.51,0:57:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不信我 你去問問你的朋友\NIf you don't believe me,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.81,0:57:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他那身衣服是用什麼做的\Nyou ask your friend what his suit is made of.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.48,0:57:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他那爪子是用什麼做的\NWhat his claws are made of.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.24,0:57:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你的父親告訴聯合國\NYour father told the UN...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.84,0:57:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,克勞偷走了你們所有的振金\Nthat Klaue stole all the vibranium you had.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.92,0:57:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,可現在 他卻說你們手上還有\NBut now he's telling me you have more.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.68,0:57:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信一個被綁在椅子上的\NAnd you believe the word
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.09,0:57:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,軍火商說的話嗎\Nof an arms dealer strapped to a chair?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.37,0:58:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那是哪裏\NWhere is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.53,0:58:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,後巷\NBack there.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.26,0:58:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你還隱瞞了什麼\NHow much more are you hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.34,0:58:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,後面情況不對\NSomething is happening out back.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.17,0:58:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下\NGet down!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.61,0:58:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下\NStand down!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.58,0:58:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,找掩護\NCover!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.68,0:58:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,手榴彈\NGrenade!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.88,0:59:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你們不是很從容的嗎\NI see you took your time, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.39,0:59:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我的國王\NMy King!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.85,0:59:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我的國王\NMy King.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.28,0:59:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,娜吉雅\NNakia.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.98,0:59:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他跳出來 擋在了我前面\NHe just jumped in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.69,0:59:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得他要撐不住了\NI don't think he'll make it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.49,0:59:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他的脊柱中槍了\NIt hit his spine.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.50,0:59:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,給我一顆基莫由珠\NGive me a Kimoyo Bead.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.13,0:59:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣應該能穩住一會兒\NThis will stabilize him for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.51,1:00:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們帶他走\NGive him to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.05,1:00:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我們能救他\NWe can save him.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.19,1:00:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的任務是帶回克勞\NOur mission was to bring back Klaue.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.09,1:00:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我們失敗了\NWe failed.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.40,1:00:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這人可是外國情報人員\NThis man is a foreign intelligence operative.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.80,1:00:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我們怎麼可以隨便帶他入境\NHow do we justify bringing him into our borders?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.57,1:00:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他替我挨了槍\NHe took a bullet for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.90,1:00:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那是他的選擇\NThat was his choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.24,1:00:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我們就應該見死不救嗎\NSo now we are just supposed to let him die?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.58,1:00:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,假如說我們救了他\NLet us consider that we heal him.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.94,1:00:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他的職責是向他的國家報告\NIt is his duty to report back to his country.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.45,1:00:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,而作為國王 你的責任是保護我們\NAnd as king, it is your duty to protect ours.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.78,1:00:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常清楚我的職責 將軍\NI'm well aware of my duties, General.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.82,1:00:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但既然知道我們能救他\NI cannot just let him die...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.82,1:00:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就不能眼睜睜地看著他死\Nknowing we can save him.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.46,1:00:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我們到底要帶他去哪兒\NWhere exactly are we taking him?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.30,1:01:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒 又來了一位需要治療的白人了\NGreat! Another broken white boy for us to fix.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.47,1:01:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這事真有意思\NThis is going to be fun.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.52,1:01:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他會活下來的\NHe will live.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.89,1:01:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,維卡必來了\NW'Kabi is here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.66,1:01:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 兄弟 克勞人呢\NWhat's going on, brother? Where is Klaue?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.57,1:01:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他不在這兒\NHe's not here.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.91,1:01:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他從我們眼皮底下溜了\NHe slipped through our hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.71,1:01:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,「溜了」？\N"Slipped"?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.85,1:01:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你父親掌權的三十年間 毫無作為\NFor 30 years, your father was in power and did nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.82,1:01:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我以為你掌權後會有所改變\NWith you, I thought it'd be different.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.02,1:01:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但似乎沒什麼兩樣\NBut it's more of the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.74,1:02:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 老大\NLet's get going, boss.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.95,1:02:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直把弄來的東西賣給中央情報局的人嗎\NYou always sell to the CIA?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.95,1:02:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,價高者得\NI sell to the highest bidder.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.02,1:02:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,別擔心 等我回到約翰內斯堡後\NBut don't you worry. When I get back to Joburg...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.45,1:02:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我會低調一點\Nand I lay low for a bit,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.76,1:02:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我保證會付你們薪水的\NI'll make sure both you guys get paid.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.39,1:02:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我不擔心錢 兄弟\NOh, I ain't worried about the money, bro.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.06,1:02:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你付得起\NI know you good for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.19,1:02:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,回程時把我們送到瓦坎達就行\NOn our way back, just drop us off in Wakanda.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.93,1:02:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你不會想去那裏的 孩子\NYou don't want to go there, boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.20,1:02:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經想好了\NYeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.97,1:02:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,放下槍\NDrop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.34,1:02:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不然你的小妮子\NOr your little Bonnie and Clyde routine
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.74,1:02:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,就沒命了\Nends today.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.31,1:02:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,立刻放下槍\NPut your gun down now!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.74,1:02:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.34,1:02:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 對不起 埃裏克 - 會沒事的\N- Sorry, Erik. - It's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.24,1:03:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的想回瓦坎達嗎\NYou really want to go to Wakanda?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.71,1:03:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他們都是野蠻人\NThey're savages.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.91,1:03:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這是他們對我們這些人幹的好事\NThis is what they do to people like us.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.28,1:03:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不在意傷疤呢\NI ain't worried about no brand.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.75,1:03:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,給你瞧\NCheck these out.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.59,1:03:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,每一個都是一條人命\NEach one is for a kill.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.26,1:03:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以盡情給自己留下傷疤\NYou can scar yourself as much as you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.16,1:03:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,對他們而言 你只是外來者\NTo them, you'll just be an outsider.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.13,1:03:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你想踏入那裏 簡直癡心妄想\NYou're crazy to think that you can walk in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.47,1:03:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我竟然以為你只是個美國瘋子\NAh, to think I saw you as some crazy American.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.69,1:04:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,都退下\NLeave us!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.87,1:04:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你沒能按計劃完成任務\NSo your mission did not go as planned.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.34,1:04:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,當年在我恩喬布叔叔身上發生了什麼\NWhat happened to my uncle N'Jobu?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.85,1:04:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我父親只是告訴我 他消失了\NMy father told me he disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.62,1:04:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但今天有個男人\NThere was a man today...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.05,1:04:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,戴著和我手上這枚一樣的戒指\Nwearing a ring identical to this one.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.66,1:04:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這不可能\NThat is not possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.06,1:04:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他從我們手中帶走了克勞 還戴著這枚戒指\NHe helped Klaue escape from us and he was wearing this ring!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.70,1:04:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我祖父的戒指！\NMy grandfather's ring!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.03,1:04:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,別說什麼不可能\NDo not tell me what is possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.74,1:04:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我真相\NTell me the truth!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.61,1:04:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,有些真相\NSome truths...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.98,1:04:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,沉重得難以承受 特查拉\Nare too much to bear, T'Challa.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.38,1:05:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,這由不得你來決定\NThat is not your choice to make.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.89,1:05:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎麼了？\NWhat happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.96,1:05:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我答應了國王保守秘密\NI promised the king to say nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.72,1:05:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我才是你的王！\NI am your king now!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.91,1:05:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你叔叔當時在美國\NYour uncle took...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.75,1:05:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,執行一項間諜任務\Na War Dog assignment in America.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.52,1:05:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你父親\NYour father...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.52,1:05:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,把我安插在那\Nplaced me there...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.99,1:05:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,暗中觀察\Nto observe...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.66,1:05:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你父親不知道的是\Nunbeknownst to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.66,1:05:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你叔叔愛上了一個美國女人\NYour uncle fell in love with an American woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.47,1:05:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他們還生了孩子\NThey had a child.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.97,1:05:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,看到外面世界的苦難\NThe hardships he saw there...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.74,1:05:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你的叔叔愈發激進\Nradicalized your uncle.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.94,1:05:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我觀察了很久\NI observed for as long as I could.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.28,1:05:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他們的總統遭到暗殺\NTheir leaders have been assassinated.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.11,1:06:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,社區裏充斥著毒品和武器\NCommunities flooded with drugs and weapons.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.58,1:06:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的黑人同胞受到壓迫 被關進監獄\NThey are overly policed and incarcerated.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.65,1:06:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,同樣的事情\NAll over the planet...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.59,1:06:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,在世界各地都在上演\Nour people suffer because
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.89,1:06:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,因為他們沒有武器去還擊\Nthey don't have the tools to fight back.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.89,1:06:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有了振金武器\NWith vibranium weapons,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.19,1:06:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他們便能推翻所有國家\Nthey could overthrow every country...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.99,1:06:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦坎達也能\Nand Wakanda could rule them all
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.90,1:06:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,讓這些國家走上正軌\Nthe right way.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.27,1:06:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他知道你的父親不會支持\NHe knew your father would not support this.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.80,1:06:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你叔叔背叛了我們\NSo, your uncle betrayed us.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.01,1:06:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.31,1:06:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他幫助克勞竊取振金\NHe helped Klaue steal the vibranium.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.35,1:06:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 不\NNo, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.81,1:06:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我命令你即刻回國\NYou will return home at once...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.42,1:06:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你將會面對議會的質詢\Nwhere you will face the Council...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.42,1:06:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,並向他們坦白你的罪行\Nand inform them of your crimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.52,1:06:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他拿武器對準我\NHe drew his weapon on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.62,1:06:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.71,1:07:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你父親殺了他的親兄弟\NYour father killed his own brother...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.84,1:07:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,救了我一命\Nto save my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.65,1:07:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這件事不要再提起\NSpeak nothing of this.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.99,1:07:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那個孩子呢？\NAnd the child?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.17,1:07:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我們丟下了他\NWe left him.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.14,1:07:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我們必須\NWe had to...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.58,1:07:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,去維持\Nmaintain...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.38,1:07:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這個謊言\Nthe lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.91,1:08:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼？\NWhat is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.88,1:08:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,只是個小禮物\NJust a little gift.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.06,1:08:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什麼人\NWho are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.82,1:09:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 這是哪兒？\NAll right, where am I?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.66,1:09:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,別這麼嚇我 殖民佬\NDon't scare me like that, colonizer!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.53,1:09:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,殖什麼？ 我是埃弗雷特\NWhat? My name is Everett.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.86,1:09:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 埃弗雷特·羅斯\NYes, I know. Everett Ross...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.70,1:09:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,前空軍飛行員 現中央情報局探員\Nformer air force pilot and now CIA.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.14,1:09:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,對\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.94,1:09:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏是瓦坎達嗎\NOkay, is this Wakanda?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.41,1:09:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這是堪薩斯\NNo, it's Kansas.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.25,1:09:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,韓國的事是什麼時候\NHow long ago was Korea?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.12,1:09:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天\NYesterday.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.35,1:09:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我不信\NI don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.59,1:09:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,槍彈傷不會奇跡般地一夜痊癒\NBullet wounds don't just magically heal overnight.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.92,1:09:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏可以\NThey do here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.22,1:09:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但不是靠魔法 而是靠科技\NBut not by magic, by technology.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.60,1:10:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,別亂碰東西 我哥哥馬上就回來\NDon't touch anything. My brother will return soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.93,1:10:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那些火車\NThese train things...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.43,1:10:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是磁懸浮列車 對吧\Nthat's magnetic levitation, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.97,1:10:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,明顯是\NObviously.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.00,1:10:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,明顯是 但我沒見過這麼...高級的\NObviously, but I've never seen it this efficient.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.01,1:10:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那些發光板是做什麼用的？\NThe light panels, what are they?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.51,1:10:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 音速穩定器 - 音速啥？\N- Sonic stabilizers. - Sonic what?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.18,1:10:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,直接高速運輸\NIn its raw form...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.55,1:10:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,原始形態的振金\Nvibranium is too dangerous
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.31,1:10:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,過於危險\Nto be transported at that speed...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.05,1:10:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我設計出了一種方法 暫時鈍化它\Nso I developed a way to temporarily deactivate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.42,1:10:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那些列車上裝著振金？\NThere's vibranium on those trains?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.16,1:11:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏到處都有振金\NThere's vibranium all around us.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.13,1:11:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你的傷也是它治好的\NThat's how I healed you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.90,1:11:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,特查拉在哪\NWhere is T'Challa?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.37,1:11:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他把他的基莫由珠關掉了\NHis Kimoyo Beads have been switched off.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.51,1:11:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不要當跟屁蟲吧 奧科燁\NWell, we are not joined at the hip, Okoye.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.84,1:11:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在邊境出現了一個男人\NA man showed up at the border
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.34,1:11:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,聲稱自己殺了克勞\Nwho claims to have killed Klaue.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.91,1:11:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.05,1:11:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,現在維卡必正帶著他前往宮殿\NW'Kabi is transporting him, as we speak, to the palace.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.55,1:11:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要找到你的哥哥\NWe need to find your brother!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.75,1:11:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一個外來者\NAn outsider?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.89,1:11:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不 是瓦坎達人\NNo, a Wakandan.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.52,1:11:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他才不是瓦坎達人\NHe's not a Wakandan.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.56,1:11:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他跟我一樣是美國人\NHe's one of ours.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.74,1:11:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他殺了他的親兄弟\NHe killed his own brother...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.11,1:11:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,然後還拋下了一個孩子\Nand left a child behind...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.38,1:11:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,孤身一人\Nwith nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.55,1:11:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼樣的國王...\NWhat kind of king...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.18,1:12:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼樣的人才會做出這樣的事？\NWhat kind of man does that?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.45,1:12:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,人無完人\NNo man is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.52,1:12:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你父親也一樣\NNot even your father.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.93,1:12:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他甚至都沒有好好安葬他\NHe didn't even give him a proper burial.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.60,1:12:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我的叔叔恩喬布背叛了我們 但是我的父親...\NMy uncle N'Jobu betrayed us, but my father...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.00,1:12:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他犯下的過錯可能更為深重\Nhe may have created something even worse.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.77,1:12:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\NHey.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.44,1:12:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,看著我\NLook at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.68,1:12:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能用你父親的罪過來定義你自己\NYou can't let your father's mistakes define who you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.18,1:12:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你要當一個怎樣的國王得由你自己決定\NYou get to decide what kind of king you are going to be.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.96,1:12:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 你得馬上過來\NBrother, you need to get here now!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.16,1:12:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,埃裏克·史蒂文斯\NErik Stevens.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.17,1:12:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,19歲就從安納波利斯大學畢業\NGraduated Annapolis age 19...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.27,1:12:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,然後拿到了麻省理工的研究生學位\NMIT for grad school.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.14,1:12:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,加入海豹突擊隊後被派往了阿富汗\NJoined the SEALs and went straight to Afghanistan...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.61,1:12:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他在那兒殺人\Nwhere he wrapped up confirmed kills,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.21,1:12:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,跟打遊戲似的\Nlike it was a video game.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.64,1:12:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,人們開始叫他 克爾芒戈\NStarted calling him Killmonger.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.58,1:13:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他還加入了美國聯合特種作戰司令部的幽靈部隊 這些傢伙可不是鬧著玩的\NHe joined a JSOC ghost unit. Now these guys are serious.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.45,1:13:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他們能秘密潛伏\NThey will drop off the grid...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.91,1:13:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,去執行暗殺\Nso they can commit assassinations
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.38,1:13:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至推翻政府\Nand take down governments.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.35,1:13:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他有暴露過他的身份信息嗎？\NDid he reveal anything about his identity?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.92,1:13:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他身上有間諜的紋身\NHe has a War Dog tattoo...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.26,1:13:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我們資料庫裏沒有他的信息\Nbut we have no record of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.50,1:13:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這個人到底是不是瓦坎達人\NIs this man Wakandan or not?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.48,1:13:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我們這是怎麼回事\NTell us what is going on.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.79,1:13:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,說話\NSpeak.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.33,1:13:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,說話\NSpeak.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.30,1:13:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在站在你們的王宮裏 告訴你們\NI'm standing in your house...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.63,1:13:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我為你們制裁了一個偷了你們振金\Nserving justice to a man
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.00,1:13:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,又謀害了你們人民的人\Nwho stole your vibranium and murdered your people.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.31,1:13:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你們的國王都沒能制裁他\NJustice your king couldn't deliver.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.94,1:14:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不在乎你有沒有把克勞帶回來\NI don't care that you brought Klaue.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.75,1:14:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我到現在還沒有殺你是因為\NOnly reason I don't kill you where you stand
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.28,1:14:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你是誰\Nis because I know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.55,1:14:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,現在 你想要什麼\NNow, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.93,1:14:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要那王位\NI want the throne.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.95,1:14:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,口氣真大\NMy goodness.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.73,1:14:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你們都坐在這舒舒服服的\NY'all sittin' up here comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.60,1:14:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺很好吧\NMust feel good.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.77,1:14:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但全球還有二十億\NIt's about two billion people
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.44,1:14:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,和我們膚色一樣的同胞\Nall over the world that looks like us.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.61,1:14:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,還活在水深火熱之中\NBut their lives are a lot harder.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.71,1:14:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦坎達有著能解放他們的工具\NWakanda has the tools to liberate 'em all.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.28,1:14:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼工具呢？\NAnd what tools are those?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.91,1:14:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,振金 你們的武器\NVibranium. Your weapons.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.78,1:14:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的武器不是用來向世界發起戰爭的\NOur weapons will not be used to wage war on the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.72,1:14:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不會拿著振金去當世界警察 去判決 審查\NIt is not our way to be judge, jury and executioner...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.56,1:14:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至處決 別國的子民的\Nfor people who are not our own.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.09,1:14:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,別國的子民？\NNot your own?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.60,1:14:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但生命不就是從這塊大陸上起源的嗎？\NBut didn't life start right here on this continent?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.30,1:14:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,全人類不都是你的子民嗎？\NSo ain't all people your people?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.77,1:15:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是全人類的國王 我是瓦坎達的國王\NI am not king of all people. I am king of Wakanda.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.37,1:15:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,而這也是我的責任\NAnd it is my responsibility
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.34,1:15:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,保證所有瓦坎達人的安危\Nto make sure our people are safe...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.38,1:15:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,以及確保振金...\Nand that vibranium does not fall
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.61,1:15:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不會落入像你這種人的手裏\Ninto the hands of a person like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.58,1:15:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,兒子\N- Mmm... - Son.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.02,1:15:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我們陪這個冒牌貨玩得夠久了\NWe have entertained this charlatan for too long.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.55,1:15:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不要答應他的要求\NReject his request.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.55,1:15:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我還沒提出要求呢\NOh, I ain't requesting nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.09,1:15:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 問問我是誰 - 你是埃裏克·史蒂文斯\N- Ask who I am. - You're Erik Stevens.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.39,1:15:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,美國黑人間諜\NAn American black operative.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.83,1:15:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,人稱克爾芒戈的傭兵\NA mercenary nicknamed Killmonger.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.67,1:15:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是你的真是身份\NThat's who you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.80,1:15:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這可不是我的名字 公主\NThat's not my name, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.03,1:15:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,問我啊 國王\NAsk me, King.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.37,1:15:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.60,1:15:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,快問我\NAsk me.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.17,1:15:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,把他帶下去\NTake him away.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.91,1:15:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底是誰？\NWho are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.12,1:15:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我是恩賈達卡 恩喬布王子之子\NI am N'Jadaka, son of Prince N'Jobu.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.50,1:15:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,恩喬布之子\NSon of N'Jobu?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.68,1:15:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我父親死的時候\NI found my daddy
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.75,1:15:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,胸前可是有豹子爪印\Nwith Panther claws in his chest!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.02,1:15:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是什麼國王的兒子 你就是一個兇手的兒子\NYou ain't the son of a king. You a son of a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.13,1:15:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你撒謊\NYou're lying!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.36,1:15:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一派胡言！ - 恐怕他說的是真的 母后\N- Lies! - I'm afraid not, Queen Mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.70,1:15:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.34,1:16:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,恩喬布的後代\NThe descendent of N'Jobu.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.87,1:16:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊 伯母\NHey, Auntie.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.81,1:16:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在行使我作為王族後裔的權利\NI'm exercising my blood right
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.81,1:16:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,向王位發出挑戰\Nto challenge for the mantles of king...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.68,1:16:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,挑戰黑豹\Nand Black Panther.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.92,1:16:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,別接受他的挑戰 特查拉\NDo not do this, T'Challa.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.35,1:16:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,身為恩喬布王子的後裔\NAs the son of Prince N'Jobu,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.75,1:16:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他有這個權利\Nhe is within his rights.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.59,1:16:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他在這裏沒有任何權利\NHe has no rights here!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.96,1:16:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,挑戰要做數周的準備工作\NThe challenge will take weeks to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.36,1:16:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,數周？ 我不需要這麼久\NWeeks? I don't need weeks.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.46,1:16:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要整個國家在場 我只需要他\NThe whole country ain't gotta be there. I just need him.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.00,1:16:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,以及一個可以幫我鬆綁的人\NAnd somebody to get me outta these chains.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.17,1:16:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,特查拉 你想清楚了嗎？\NT'Challa, what do you know of this?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.51,1:16:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我接受你的挑戰\NI accept your challenge.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.00,1:17:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他不可能打敗特查拉的\NHe'll never beat T'Challa.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.63,1:17:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他就應該在上次挑戰的時候來\NHe should've just come to the first challenge
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.77,1:17:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,一次性搞定\Nand gotten it over with.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.58,1:17:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,國王現將\NThe king will now have the strength
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.94,1:17:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,黑豹之力移除\Nof the Black Panther stripped away.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.75,1:17:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,羅斯探員在哪\NWhere is Agent Ross?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.11,1:17:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我把他關在辦公室了 他跑不了的\NI locked him in the office. He's not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.49,1:18:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這是你最後的機會\NThis is your last chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.43,1:18:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,放下武器\NThrow down your weapons,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.16,1:18:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣我們還有商量的餘地\Nand we can handle this another way.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.17,1:18:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我的一生都在為這一時刻做準備\NI lived my entire life waitin' for this moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.48,1:18:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我艱苦訓練 謊話連天 殺人無數\NI trained, I lied, I killed...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.38,1:18:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,就是為了到這裏\Njust to get here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.78,1:18:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我征戰過美國 阿富汗\NI killed in America, Afghanistan...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.36,1:18:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,伊拉克\NIraq.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.86,1:18:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我剝奪生命\NI took life from my own brothers and sisters
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.83,1:18:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,剝奪來自這片陸地的兄弟姐妹們的生命\Nright here on this continent.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.73,1:18:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,殺了這麼多人\NAnd all this death...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.43,1:18:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就只是為了殺你\Njust so I could kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.44,1:18:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,挑戰現在開始\NLet the challenge begin.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.29,1:19:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,投降！\NYield!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.91,1:20:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,幹掉他 特查拉！\NSnap out of it, T'Challa!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.70,1:20:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,快啊 站起來\NCome on, get up.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.97,1:20:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,來啊\NCome here.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.74,1:20:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這是為了我的父親\NThis is for my father.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.54,1:20:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,埃裏克！\NErik!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.54,1:20:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 祖瑞 不 - 住手\N- Zuri, no. - Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.61,1:20:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 祖瑞 - 祖瑞 不\N- Zuri! - Zuri, don't!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.91,1:20:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是我讓你的父親喪命\NI am the cause of your father's death.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.25,1:20:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不是他\NNot him.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.85,1:20:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,殺我\NTake me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.25,1:20:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你們倆都要死 詹姆斯叔叔\NI'll take you both, Uncle James.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.86,1:20:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.59,1:20:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不！ 不！\NNo! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.70,1:20:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,祖瑞 不\NZuri, no!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.20,1:20:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.50,1:20:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不！祖瑞！ 祖瑞！\NNo! No! Zuri! Zuri!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.47,1:21:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不！ 不！\NNo! No!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.51,1:21:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是你們的國王？\NIs this your king? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.95,1:21:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是你們的國王？\NIs this your king?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.66,1:21:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,黑豹\NThe Black Panther,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.12,1:21:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,本應是帶領你們走向未來的人\Nwho's supposed to lead you into the future?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.09,1:21:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,加油 哥哥！\NCome on, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.83,1:21:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真的沒有辦法了嗎？\NIs there nothing that can be done?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.66,1:21:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就他？\NHim?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.73,1:21:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,還想保護你們？\NHe's supposed to protect you?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.42,1:21:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不要 - 不要\N- No. - No!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.39,1:21:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.46,1:21:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我才是你們的王\NNah. I'm your king.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.93,1:21:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不！ - 我們得馬上離開\N- No! No! - We have to go now!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.80,1:22:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,母后 我們走！\NQueen Mother, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.54,1:22:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,太后和舒莉 她們安全嗎？\NThe Queen Mother and Shuri, they are safe?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.64,1:22:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,安全\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.24,1:22:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.68,1:22:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我們得馬上去找她們\NWe should get to them immediately.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.58,1:22:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能\NI cannot
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.48,1:22:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.35,1:22:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧 我的心和你在一起\NThough my heart is with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.02,1:22:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不能把我們的國家\NWe cannot turn over our nation to a man
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.32,1:22:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,交給一個才出現了幾個小時的人\Nwho showed up here only hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.16,1:22:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他有皇室血統\NHe is of royal blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.29,1:22:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他殺了特查拉！ - 那是在格鬥儀式中\N- He killed T'Challa! - In ritual combat.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.83,1:22:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那還不是一樣？\NDoes that really matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.23,1:23:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你是瓦坎達最出色的戰士\NYou are the greatest warrior Wakanda has.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.47,1:23:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,幫我在他強大起來之前推翻他\NHelp me overthrow him before he becomes too strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.64,1:23:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,推翻？\NOverthrow?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.68,1:23:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,娜奇雅\NNakia!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.14,1:23:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是那種來去隨意的間諜\NI'm not a spy who can come and go as they so choose!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.55,1:23:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我所效忠的是那個王座 不管是誰坐在上面\NI am loyal to that throne, no matter who sits upon it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.82,1:23:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你效忠的是什麼？\NWhat are you loyal to?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.96,1:23:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我愛他\NI loved him.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.83,1:23:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我也愛我的國家\NI loved my country, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.20,1:23:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就應該效忠你的國家\NThen you serve your country.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.37,1:23:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我要拯救我的國家\NNo. I save my country.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.75,1:23:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,出什麼事了\NWhat's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.05,1:23:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,國王死了\NThe king is dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.68,1:23:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你要不想跟他為伍就跟我走\NCome with me, unless you want to join him.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.80,1:24:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,先是爸爸\NFirst Baba.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.68,1:24:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,現在輪到我的哥哥\NAnd now my brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.81,1:24:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽 我們甚至都沒能安葬他\NMama, we didn't even get to bury him.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.19,1:24:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是我 - 娜奇雅 這人是誰？\N- It's me. - Nakia. Who is this man?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.23,1:24:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他是特查拉的朋友 他救過我的命\NHe's a friend of T'Challa's. He saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.23,1:24:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,奧科燁呢？\NWhere's Okoye?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.33,1:24:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,奧科燁沒有來\NOkoye is not coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.53,1:24:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,她和多拉米拉吉護衛隊會效忠新王\NShe and the Dora Milaje will serve the new king.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.48,1:24:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,在這等我\NWait here.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.28,1:24:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的瓦坎達怎麼了\NWhat has happened to our Wakanda?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.35,1:25:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,讓心形草\NAllow the Heart-Shaped Herb...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.59,1:25:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,賦予你黑豹的力量\Nto give you the powers of the Black Panther...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.69,1:25:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,帶你前往先祖的世界\Nand take you to the Ancestral Plane.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.69,1:26:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎麼跟你說的 別翻我的東西\NWhat did I tell you about going into my things?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.77,1:26:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你找到了什麼\NWhat did you find?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.14,1:26:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你的家\NYour home.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.74,1:27:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我給你鑰匙 就是希望你有一天能看到它\NI gave you a key hoping that you might see it someday.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.88,1:27:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 那裏的日落\NYes. The sunsets there
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.85,1:27:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是全世界最美的\Nare the most beautiful in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.15,1:27:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但我擔心你不會受歡迎\NBut I fear you still may not be welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.03,1:27:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼？\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.16,1:27:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他們會說你走丟了\NThey will say you are lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.37,1:27:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但我就在這裏啊\NBut I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.84,1:27:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不為我流淚嗎\NNo tears for me?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.84,1:27:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,每個人都難逃一死\NEverybody dies.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.38,1:27:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏的生活就是這樣\NIt's just life around here.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.52,1:27:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧我都做了些什麼\NWell, look at what I have done.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.89,1:27:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我早就該帶你回去的\NI should've taken you back long ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.36,1:27:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,而現在 我們都被拋棄在這兒了\NInstead, we are both abandoned here.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.80,1:28:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,也許走丟了的是你的家才對\NWell, maybe your home is the one that's lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.48,1:28:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他們才找不到我們\NThat's why they can't find us.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.82,1:28:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,呼吸 呼吸 陛下 呼吸\NBreathe! Breathe, My King, breathe.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.49,1:28:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,呼吸 呼吸\NBreathe. Breathe. Breathe.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.64,1:28:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是心形草的作用嗎\NThe Heart-Shaped Herb did that?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.51,1:28:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,全部的都在這麼\NThis all of it?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.71,1:28:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,當下一任國王繼位時\NYes. So when it comes time for another king,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.85,1:28:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就能準備好\Nwe will be ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.49,1:28:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,下一任國王？\NAnother king?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.79,1:28:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,去把那些都燒了\NYeah, go ahead and burn all that.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.02,1:28:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,陛下 我們不能這麼做 這是我們的傳統\NMy King, we cannot do that. It is our tradition...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.43,1:29:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我讓你做什麼 你就得做什麼\NWhen I tell you to do something, I mean that shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.34,1:29:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,全燒了\NBurn it all!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.09,1:29:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你們知道麼 在我的家鄉\NYou know, where I'm from...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.46,1:29:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,黑人鬧革命的時候\Nwhen black folks started revolutions,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.63,1:30:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他們沒有武器\Nthey never had the firepower...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.56,1:30:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,也沒有資源去反抗壓迫者\Nor the resources to fight their oppressors.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.33,1:30:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那時瓦坎達在哪裏呢？\NWhere was Wakanda?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.14,1:30:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這種局面以後將不復存在\NYeah, all that ends today.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.84,1:30:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我們在地球上每個國家裏都安插有間諜\NWe got spies embedded in every nation on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.28,1:30:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,全都已經就位\NAlready in place.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.18,1:30:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道殖民者是怎麼想的\NI know how colonizers think.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.58,1:30:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我們要以其人之道還治其人之身\NSo we're gonna use their own strategy against 'em.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.02,1:30:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我們會把振金武器送到我們的間諜手中\NWe're gonna send vibranium weapons out to our War Dogs.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.06,1:30:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他們會武裝全世界被壓迫的人民\NThey'll arm oppressed people all over the world...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.96,1:30:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣他們才能站起來反抗 殺掉掌權者\Nso they can finally rise up and kill those in power.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.63,1:30:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,和他們的孩子\NAnd their children.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.43,1:30:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,以及所有他們的同夥\NAnd anyone else who takes their side.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.16,1:30:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是時候向他們展示我們真正的實力了\NIt's time they know the truth about us!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.07,1:30:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是戰士\NWe're warriors!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.70,1:30:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,世界秩序將被重新建立 而這一次 將由我們來掌權\NThe world's gonna start over, and this time, we're on top.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.27,1:30:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦坎達將成為日不落帝國\NThe sun will never set on the Wakandan empire.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.58,1:30:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦坎達之所以能在世界中存在這麼久\NWakanda has survived for so long...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:52.25,1:30:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,正是因為我們只在絕對必要的時候才打仗\Nby fighting when only absolutely necessary.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.82,1:30:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦坎達過去是這樣的 沒錯\NWakanda survived in the past this way, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.95,1:31:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但世界在改變啊 將軍\NBut the world is changing, General.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.93,1:31:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,長老們 瓦坎達的優勢受到挑戰\NElders, it is getting smaller.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.60,1:31:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,外面的世界正在迎頭趕上\NThe outside world is catching up...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.63,1:31:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不久之後 它要麼征服別人\Nand soon it will be the conquerors
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.70,1:31:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,要麼就被別人征服\Nor the conquered.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.74,1:31:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我寧願做征服者\NI'd rather be the former.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.61,1:31:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你們聽到命令了 開始行動吧\NYou heard your orders. Let's get to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.91,1:31:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要去哪來著\NSo where are we going again?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.21,1:31:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要把心形草\NWe're taking the Heart-Shaped Herb
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.18,1:31:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,帶到賈巴裏的領地\Nto Jabariland.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.32,1:31:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,心形草？ 那是什麼？\NHeart-Shaped Herb? What is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.95,1:31:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,它會增強服用者的能力\NIt gives whoever takes it heightened abilities.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.62,1:31:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,正是它讓特查拉變得那麼強大的\NIt's what made T'Challa so strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.92,1:31:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,娜奇雅\NNakia.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.26,1:31:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜歡這樣\NI don't like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.30,1:31:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,心形草是屬於我們的\NThe Herb belongs to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.03,1:31:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我們這樣可能會讓姆巴庫成為更為可怕的惡魔\NWe may be creating a bigger monster with M'Baku.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.48,1:31:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,娜奇雅 你應該給自己用\NNakia, you should take it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.75,1:32:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是個間諜 手上沒有軍隊\NI am a spy with no army.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.55,1:32:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我一點機會都沒有的\NI wouldn't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.19,1:32:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我們走吧\NWe'll go.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.30,1:32:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪\NOh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.77,1:32:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,該死\NOh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.34,1:32:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,低頭 冷靜\NLook down. Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.38,1:32:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,舒莉\NShuri.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.61,1:32:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,低頭\NLook down.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.42,1:33:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我的兒子\NMy son...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.65,1:33:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在格鬥儀式中被謀殺了\Nwas murdered in ritual combat.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.76,1:33:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 格鬥的過程公平嗎 - 公平 但\N- Were the odds fair? - Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.03,1:33:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那就不是謀殺 而是戰敗\NSo it was less a murder than a defeat.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.83,1:33:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 這輪不到你來說！- 安靜\N- Do not rub our noses in it! - Silence!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.86,1:33:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏我說了算 小姑娘\NI make the pronouncements here, girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.67,1:33:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,聽我說 陛下 新王是一個...\NLook, uh, Your Highness, the new king is a U.S...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.41,1:33:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,新王...\NThe new king...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.25,1:33:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你不准說話\NYou cannot talk!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.55,1:33:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,再多說一個字\NOne more word,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.92,1:33:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我就把你餵給我的孩子們\Nand I will feed you to my children.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.46,1:33:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,開玩笑的 我們是素食主義者\NI'm kidding. We are vegetarians.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.87,1:33:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,偉大的人猿姆巴庫\NGreat Gorilla M'Baku...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.64,1:34:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是我們來這兒的原因\Nthis is why we are here.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.71,1:34:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,把這個獻給你\NTo offer this to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.65,1:34:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一個外來者坐在了我們的王位上\NAn outsider sits on our throne.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.08,1:34:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你能幫我們阻止他\NOnly you can help us stop him.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.64,1:34:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我來\NCome with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.36,1:34:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,這不可能\NImpossible!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.30,1:34:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他還活著嗎\NIs he breathing?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.26,1:34:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他昏迷了 只剩一口氣\NHe's in a coma. Barely clinging to life.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.57,1:35:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的一個漁夫\NOne of our fishermen found him
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.17,1:35:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,在河邊發現了他\Nat the edge of the river border.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.01,1:35:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,並把他帶到了我這裏\NHe brought him to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.57,1:35:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼把他埋在雪裏？\NWhy do you have him in the snow?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.31,1:35:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,這是唯一\NIt is the only thing keeping him
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.71,1:35:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,能挽回他性命的辦法\Nfrom joining the ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.98,1:35:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我們得把他帶回實驗室 在那我就可以救活他\NWe need to get him to my lab. I can heal him there.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.65,1:35:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,帶他走吧 他撐不了多久的\NTake him. He'll be dead in seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.85,1:35:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,娜奇雅 草藥\NNakia, the Herb.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.47,1:35:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,列祖列宗在上\NI call upon the ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.81,1:35:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,芭絲特女神在上\NI call upon Bast.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.18,1:35:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,吾與吾子 特查拉\NI am here with my son, T'Challa.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.38,1:35:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,拯救他\NHeal him.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.49,1:35:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我們必須把他埋起來 蓋住他 蓋住他\NWe must bury him. Cover him. Cover him!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.80,1:36:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.05,1:36:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,願祖上榮光永存\NPraise the ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.56,1:36:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,願祖上榮光永存\NPraise the ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.68,1:36:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,願祖上榮光永存\NPraise the ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.19,1:36:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,願祖上榮光永存\NPraise the ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.55,1:36:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,醒來吧 特查拉\NWake up, T'Challa.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.52,1:36:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,醒來吧\NWake up.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.19,1:36:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我的兒子\NMy son.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.80,1:36:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,時間到了 你是時候回家\NThe time has come for you to come home...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.03,1:36:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,與我團聚了\Nand be reunited with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.39,1:36:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.99,1:36:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你不帶那個男孩回家？\NWhy didn't you bring the boy home?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.86,1:37:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼 爸爸？\NWhy, Baba?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.33,1:37:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他...\NHe...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.26,1:37:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我選擇忽略掉這一事實\NHe was the truth I chose to omit.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.80,1:37:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你不應該拋棄他的\NYou were wrong to abandon him.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.64,1:37:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我選擇了我的人民\NI chose my people.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.41,1:37:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我選擇了瓦坎達\NI chose Wakanda.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.98,1:37:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的未來決定於...\NOur future depended...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.01,1:37:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你錯了！\NYou were wrong!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.78,1:37:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你們全都錯了！\NAll of you were wrong!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.02,1:37:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,錯就錯在我們對於外面的世界視而不見\NTo turn your backs on the rest of the world!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.22,1:37:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,對外面世界的恐懼\NWe let the fear of our discovery
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.23,1:37:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,阻礙了我們做出正確的選擇\Nstop us from doing what is right!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.96,1:37:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不能再這樣下去了！\NNo more!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.07,1:37:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能和你待在這\NI cannot stay here with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.51,1:37:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,只要他還坐在王座上我就不能安息\NI cannot rest while he sits on the throne.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.31,1:37:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我們自己創造出來的怪物\NHe is a monster of our own making.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.08,1:37:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我必須要奪回王位 我一定要！\NI must take the mantle back. I must!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.59,1:38:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我必須糾正這些錯誤\NI must right these wrongs.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.00,1:38:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,可以給我個毯子嗎？\NDo you have a blanket?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.37,1:38:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,克爾芒戈獲得了\NKillmonger has the full support
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.51,1:38:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,軍隊的全力支持\Nof our military.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.55,1:38:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,而且...\NAnd he burned the garden of the Heart-Shaped Herb.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.95,1:38:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他還把心形草全都燒光了\NOf course he did.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.12,1:38:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他當然會 他就是被這麼訓練的\NThat's what he was trained to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.09,1:38:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他的組織曾經和中情局合作\NHis unit used to work with the CIA
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.85,1:38:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,在別國製造混亂\Nto destabilize foreign countries.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.66,1:38:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他們總是在政權交替時趁人之危\NThey would always strike at transitions of power...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.06,1:38:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,比如大選年 或部族首領死亡\Nlike an election year, or the death of a monarch.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.33,1:38:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他們就掌控政府 軍隊\NYou get control of government, the military...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.96,1:38:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 衝著我們的資源來的 - 沒錯\N- Our resources. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.13,1:38:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我們偉大的部落\NThe Great Mound.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.27,1:38:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的振金 我的發明\NOur vibranium, all of my designs.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.14,1:38:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他會把我們的武器送到世界各地\NHe will send our weapons all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.14,1:38:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你必須護送她們安全離開瓦坎達\NYou must get them out of Wakanda safely.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.71,1:38:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什麼？ - 那你呢？\N- What? - What about you?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.45,1:39:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,挑戰必須繼續\NThe challenge will have to continue.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.55,1:39:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,特查拉 我們不會離開瓦坎達的\NT'Challa, we will not leave Wakanda.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.12,1:39:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,保護你的安全是我的責任\NIt is my duty to keep you safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.25,1:39:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他掌控了我們的技術\NIf he gets control of our technology,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.92,1:39:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我們無處可逃\Nnowhere will be safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.91,1:39:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,黑豹還活著\NThe Black Panther lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.62,1:39:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,而等他為瓦坎達的命運戰鬥時\NAnd when he fights for the fate of Wakanda...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.02,1:39:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我將在他身邊\NI will be right there beside him.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.76,1:39:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\NAs will I.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.29,1:39:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我也加入\NI'm in, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.29,1:39:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼 人多力量大嘛\NWhat? You're gonna need all the help you can get.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.80,1:39:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你們完事了沒？\NAre you done?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.27,1:39:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你們到底完事了沒有？\NAre you done?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.74,1:39:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,可以讓我跟姆巴庫首領單獨談談嗎？\NCould you give me and Lord M'Baku a moment?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.68,1:40:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.32,1:40:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我欠你的\NI owed you a great debt.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.56,1:40:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,一命抵一命\NA life for a life.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.16,1:40:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你我就兩清了\NConsider it paid.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.33,1:40:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,請允許我母親留在你這裏\NPlease allow my mother to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.33,1:40:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,她不會有事的 我向你保證\NNo harm will come to her. I give you my word.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.40,1:40:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 我也能帶兵打仗的\NYou know, I could use an army as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.27,1:40:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你當然能\NI bet you could.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.04,1:40:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但沒門\NBut no.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.78,1:40:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會讓賈巴裏人為你的事賣命\NI will give no Jabari lives towards your cause.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.81,1:40:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我們的事\NIt is our cause.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.92,1:40:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是我們共同的事 - 我們？\N- It is for all of us. - Oh, us?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.42,1:40:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我們？ 你是幾個世紀以來第一個來我們這的王\NUs? You are the first king to come here in centuries...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.95,1:40:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,現在你跟我說 「我們」？\Nand now you speak of "us"?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.16,1:40:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我無法替先王們開脫\NI cannot speak for past kings.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.40,1:40:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但如今一個敵人正坐在王位上\NBut an enemy sits on the throne right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.43,1:40:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你我都知道振金的威力\NWe both know the power of vibranium.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.07,1:40:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如果克爾芒戈掌控了它\NIf Killmonger gains control of it,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.21,1:41:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得他下一個會找上誰？\Nwho do you think he will come for next?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.95,1:41:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不會幫你\NWe will not help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.68,1:41:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都在按計劃進行\NEverything is on schedule.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.15,1:41:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,間諜們都接到通知了嗎？\NHave the spies been alerted?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.42,1:41:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 有一些間諜對於我們的新任務表示反對\NYes. Some resistance to our new mission.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.02,1:41:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但倫敦 紐約 和香港的間諜組織\NBut the War Dogs in London,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.49,1:41:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,都隨時待命\NNew York and Hong Kong are standing by.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.06,1:41:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我們先攻打那些地方\NWe'll strike there first.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.89,1:41:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人會審時度勢的\NThe others'll come around.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.86,1:41:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,看看這個\NLook at this.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.30,1:41:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這個手持超音速炮的威力\NA handheld sonic cannon,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.43,1:41:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,足以對抗坦克\Npowerful enough to stop a tank...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.07,1:42:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,金屬探測器都追查不到\Nuntraceable by metal detectors.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.90,1:42:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我們有幾千個\NAnd we got thousands of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.87,1:42:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,世界終將明白我們的真正實力\NThe world's gonna find out exactly who we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.81,1:42:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他還活著\NHe lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.01,1:42:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,恩賈達卡\NN'Jadaka!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.12,1:42:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你想怎樣？\NWassup?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.65,1:42:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我還沒投降！\NI never yielded!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.05,1:42:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,而且如你所見 我也沒死！\NAnd as you can see, I am not dead!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.26,1:42:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,挑戰什麼的已經結束了\NAll that challenge shit is over with!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.39,1:42:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我是王\NI'm the king now!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.70,1:43:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,讓飛機起飛 繼續任務\NGet those planes in the air! Carry out the mission!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.37,1:43:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舒莉 就現在 - 收到\N- Shuri, now. - Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.34,1:43:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,快走  快走 快點 羅斯\NGo, go, go! Come on, Ross!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.25,1:43:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,維卡必 幹掉這隻小丑\NW'Kabi, man, kill this clown.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.72,1:43:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,維卡必 挑戰還沒結束\NW'Kabi, the challenge is not complete.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.02,1:43:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我們該怎麼辦\NWhat will we do?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.70,1:43:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,邊疆部落\NBorder Tribe!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.81,1:43:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你！\NYou!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.74,1:43:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你的心中怨氣太深\NYour heart is so full of hatred...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.35,1:43:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你不適合當王！\Nyou are not fit to be a king!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.72,1:43:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧\NCome on!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.82,1:43:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尤 保護國王\NAyo, the king!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.37,1:44:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,防禦陣型\NShields!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.58,1:44:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,維卡必 停下來！\NW'Kabi, stop this!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.25,1:44:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,快停下！\NStop this now!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.99,1:44:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.08,1:45:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,娜奇雅和我將會用這個控制皇家戰機\NNakia and I will get control of the Royal Talon with this.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.98,1:45:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 我做什麼\NSo what do I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.49,1:45:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你要駕駛它\NYou'll have to fly it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.46,1:45:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什麼？ - 你曾是個厲害的飛行員\N- What? - You were a great pilot.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.52,1:45:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心 我會指導你的\NDon't worry, I'll guide you through it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.69,1:45:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,就像開摩托飛艇一樣\NIt's just like riding a hoverbike.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.56,1:45:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？ 你們還有摩托飛艇嗎？\NWhat? You guys have hoverbikes?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.43,1:45:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 娜奇雅 穿上這個\NHey, Nakia, take that.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.20,1:45:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我又不是戰士 - 就穿上吧 這是戰甲！\N- I'm not a Dora. - Just put it on, it's armor!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.80,1:45:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,快來\NCome!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.17,1:45:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好運 羅斯探員\NGood luck, Agent Ross!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.44,1:45:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道該怎麼用...這個東西\NYeah, I don't know what I'm doing with this.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.81,1:45:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我們都指望你了\NWe're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.86,1:46:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦坎達萬歲\NWakanda forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.53,1:46:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,上啊！\NCome on!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.15,1:46:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,快走\NGo, go!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.95,1:46:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,遠程駕駛系統啟動\NRemote piloting system activated.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.09,1:46:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\NMy God.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.12,1:46:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我幫你改成美式機艙了 快坐進去\NI made it American style for you. Get in.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.39,1:46:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.17,1:46:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好！\NYes!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.04,1:47:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,快上 我們不能讓那些武器出了瓦坎達的邊境\NGo! We can't let those weapons get beyond Wakanda.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.81,1:47:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 我馬上\NAll right, I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.97,1:47:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,鎖住！\NLock!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.89,1:47:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,拿下\NGet him down!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.81,1:47:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,摘掉他的項鏈\NGet the necklace!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.85,1:47:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,摘掉他的項鏈！\NGet the necklace!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.28,1:47:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦坎達萬歲！\NWakanda forever!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.99,1:47:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 舒莉 我追到他們了 我該怎麼做？\NOkay, Shuri. I got 'em. What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.52,1:47:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,把他們打下來啊 天才！\NShoot them down, genius!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.16,1:47:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.66,1:47:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我盡力而為吧\NHere goes nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.10,1:48:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 一架\NAll right, got them.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.48,1:48:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,該死\NOh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.64,1:48:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,該死\NShit, shit, shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.67,1:48:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮\NNice!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.94,1:49:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,舒莉！\NShuri!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.41,1:49:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 公主？\NWhat's up, Princess?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.85,1:49:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你永遠成不了真正的王\NYou'll never be a true king.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.08,1:49:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥！\NBrother!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.22,1:49:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,舒莉\NShuri.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.99,1:49:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥！\NBrother!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.69,1:49:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,把最底下的火車開起來\NTurn on the train on the bottom track.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.36,1:49:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,穩定器會讓你的戰衣失效的的\NThe stabilizers will deactivate your suit!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.72,1:49:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你到時候就沒有保護了\NYou won't have protection!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.33,1:50:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那他也不會有\NNeither will he.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.73,1:50:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOkay!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.09,1:50:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我根本不需要這身衣服來殺你\NI don't need a suit to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:28.62,1:50:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你的統治結束了\NYour reign is over!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.92,1:50:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你以為你能穩居王位\NYou sat up here, safe and protected.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.73,1:50:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是想看著我們\NYou want to see us become
Dialogue: 0,1:50:33.13,1:50:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,變成那些你憎恨的人一樣\Njust like the people you hate so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:35.20,1:50:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就像那些殖民者一樣\NDivide and conquer the land as they did!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.13,1:50:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不 這是我從敵人那兒學到的 以牙還牙\NNah, I learn from my enemies. Beat them at they own game.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.80,1:50:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你已經變得跟他們一樣！\NYou have become them!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:41.24,1:50:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你會毀了這世界的 包括瓦坎達在內\NYou will destroy the world, Wakanda included!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.87,1:50:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這個世界奪走了我的一切！\NThe world took everything away from me!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.81,1:50:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,一切我所愛的東西！\NEverything I ever loved!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.54,1:50:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我會確保人人平等\NBut I'mma make sure we're even.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:49.04,1:50:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我要找到所有\NI'mma track down anyone who would
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.21,1:50:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕對你只有一絲忠誠的人！\Neven think about being loyal to you!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.95,1:50:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,全都宰了埋了\NAnd I'm gonna put they ass in the dirt
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.48,1:50:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就埋在祖瑞的邊上！\Nright next to Zuri!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:56.62,1:50:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,娜奇雅！\NNakia!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:01.12,1:51:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你沒事吧？ - 我沒事 你呢？\N- Are you all right? - I'm okay. You?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:03.29,1:51:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 沒事 - 我們走\N- Yes. - Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.00,1:51:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,舒莉 我甩掉了一架敵機 但是還有兩架在我屁股後面\NShuri, I've lost one of them, but two are on my tail.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.77,1:51:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼鬼？\NShit. What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:18.07,1:51:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,實驗室正遭受攻擊\NThe lab is under attack.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.61,1:51:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？ 哪？\NWhat? Where?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.71,1:51:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,停止全息影像\NDeactivating hologram.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:26.48,1:51:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,羅斯 你必須馬上離開那\NRoss, you have to get out of there, now!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.02,1:51:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我還剩多久時間？\NHow long have I got?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.09,1:51:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,玻璃完整度 50%\NGlass integrity is at 50%.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.96,1:51:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,把我接回去\NPut me back in.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:37.33,1:51:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,羅斯！羅斯！\NRoss! Ross!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.82,1:51:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,馬上投降！\NSurrender now!
Dialogue: 0,1:51:59.58,1:52:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你有三秒鐘放下你的武器\NYou have three seconds to lay down your weapon!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.82,1:52:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,一！\NOne!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:04.22,1:52:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,二！\NTwo!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:15.07,1:52:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你們見識見識賈巴裏的力量吧！\NWitness the might of the Jabari firsthand!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.35,1:53:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,玻璃完整度 15%\NGlass integrity is at 15%.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:11.72,1:53:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- 武器嚴重損毀 - 該死\N- Critical weapons failure. - Shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:18.87,1:53:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,舒莉 最後一艘貨船\NHey, Shuri! The last cargo ship
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.63,1:53:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就快到邊境了\Nis almost at the border...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:21.97,1:53:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他們現在用某種電纜把我困住了\Nbut they got me trapped with some kind of cables.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.24,1:53:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,把雙手交叉放在胸前\NMake an X with your arms!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:25.30,1:53:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,音速超頻啟動\NSonic Overload initiated.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:28.51,1:53:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,現在 放開\NNow break it!
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.42,1:53:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,五秒後重啟系統...\NSystem rebooting in five...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:40.92,1:53:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,4 3\Nfour, three...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.32,1:53:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,2 1\Ntwo, one.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:45.49,1:53:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,系統重啟完成\NSystem rebooted.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.84,1:54:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,耶！ 我們成功了！\NYes! We did it!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.24,1:54:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 現在趕緊離開那\NGreat! Now get out of there!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.93,1:54:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,沖\NCharge!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.11,1:54:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,放下你的武器\NDrop your weapon!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:38.01,1:54:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你會殺了我嗎 親愛的？\NWould you kill me, my love?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.48,1:54:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,為了瓦坎達？\NFor Wakanda?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:45.09,1:54:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,毫無疑問\NWithout question!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.87,1:55:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,到此為止了 表弟\NThis is it for you, Cousin.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:58.09,1:55:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,有兩下子啊\NHell of a move!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:20.89,1:56:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸說\NMy pop said Wakanda was
Dialogue: 0,1:56:22.42,1:56:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦坎達是他見過最美麗的地方\Nthe most beautiful thing he ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:27.66,1:56:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他答應我 說總有一天他會帶我去看看\NHe promised he was gonna show it to me one day.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.00,1:56:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你能相信嗎\NYou believe that?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:34.57,1:56:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一個奧克蘭的小屁孩\NKid from Oakland,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:35.53,1:56:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,整天活在童話故事裏\Nrunning around believing in fairy tales.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:25.95,1:57:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很美\NIt's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:42.04,1:57:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,也許我們還能治好你\NMaybe we can still heal you.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:46.91,1:57:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼？\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.88,1:57:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,然後你就可以把我關起來？\NSo you can just lock me up?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:55.45,1:57:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,才不要\NNah.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:58.89,1:58:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,把我葬在海裏\NJust bury me in the ocean...
Dialogue: 0,1:58:00.55,1:58:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就像我那些從船上跳海的先祖們一樣\Nwith my ancestors that jumped from the ships.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:03.86,1:58:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,因為他們知道死也比被奴役好\N'Cause they knew death was better than bondage.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:32.01,1:59:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:35.02,1:59:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你救了我\NYou saved me.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:37.42,1:59:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你救了我的家人\NYou saved my family.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:41.89,1:59:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的國家\NOur nation.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:43.36,1:59:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用謝我什麼\NThere's nothing to thank me for.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:45.96,1:59:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我們的...\NIt is our duty to...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:50.90,1:59:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,為我愛的事物去戰鬥是我的義務\NIt was my duty to fight for what I love.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:54.87,1:59:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我就應該...\NI should've...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:02.45,2:00:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能怪我 我差點就死了\NYou can't blame me, I almost died.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:08.35,2:00:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,留下\NStay.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:12.12,2:00:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我有個辦法\NI think I know a way
Dialogue: 0,2:00:13.39,2:00:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,仍可以讓你實現你的願望\Nyou can still fulfill your calling.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:16.93,2:00:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,留下吧\NPlease stay.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:51.36,2:00:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他要上籃了 他要上籃了\NOh, he moves it! He moves it!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:53.30,2:00:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 誰負責防守他的 - 進了\N- Who man is that? - Bucket!
Dialogue: 0,2:00:55.17,2:00:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,小菜一碟\NEasy.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:59.17,2:01:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你之前說\NWhen you said you would take me
Dialogue: 0,2:01:00.51,2:01:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,要帶我到加州\Nto California for the first time...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:02.58,2:01:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為你指的是讓我參加科切拉音樂節\NI thought you meant Coachella...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:04.88,2:01:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,或者是迪士尼樂園\Nor Disneyland.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:06.98,2:01:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼是這裏？\NWhy here?
Dialogue: 0,2:01:11.42,2:01:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是我們的父親殺了我們叔叔的地方\NThis is where our father killed our uncle.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:20.16,2:01:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏要被拆掉了\NThey're tearing it down.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:23.03,2:01:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\NGood.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:24.16,2:01:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏不會被拆掉的\NThey are not tearing it down.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:27.27,2:01:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我買下了這棟樓\NI bought this building.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:31.00,2:01:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,還有那棟\NAnd that building.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:33.61,2:01:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,以及那邊那棟\NAnd that one over there.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:36.58,2:01:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這裏將成為第一個\NThis will be the first
Dialogue: 0,2:01:37.88,2:01:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦坎達國際援助中心\NWakandan International Outreach Center.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:41.55,2:01:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,娜奇雅會負責監管社會援助\NNakia will oversee the social outreach.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:45.09,2:01:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,而你會負責進行\NAnd you will spearhead
Dialogue: 0,2:01:46.35,2:01:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次科學與信息交流活動\Nthe science and information exchange.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:49.26,2:01:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你在逗我嗎\NYou're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:51.73,2:01:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,有嗎？\NEh?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:03.27,2:02:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿哥們 那是什麼\NHey, yo. Man, what the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:06.34,2:02:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這是布加迪牌的宇宙飛船吧\NThat's like a Bugatti spaceship!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:08.04,2:02:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就這麼憑空出現了 你看到了嗎？\NBro, it came out of nowhere. Did y'all see that?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:14.02,2:02:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:17.02,2:02:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,快來看啊\NCheck it out, bro.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:17.95,2:02:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,把這個帶回家呀\NWe can take this back to the house.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:20.69,2:02:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,開著這個去上學啊\NPull up to school in this.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:21.89,2:02:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 聽著 我們可以把這個給拆了然後賣掉\NLook, we can break it apart. We can sell it.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:24.06,2:02:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,在淘寶上賣\NOn eBay.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:25.09,2:02:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,一片就能賣上個幾十萬\NEverybody get, like, a million apiece.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:26.46,2:02:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我如果是你們我就不會這麼做\NI wouldn't do that if I were you guys.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:27.76,2:02:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你從哪來的？ - 瓦坎達\N- Where you come from? - From Wakanda.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:28.76,2:02:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦坎達是哪？\NWhat is a Wakanda?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:30.13,2:02:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 你！\NHey, yo!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:31.90,2:02:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,這是你的？\NThis yours?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:36.90,2:02:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你...\NWho...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:38.47,2:02:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你是誰？\NWho are you?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:25.64,2:05:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我是國王特查拉\NMy name is King T'Challa...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:27.92,2:05:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,特查卡國王之子\Nson of King T'Chaka.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:30.15,2:05:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我是瓦坎達的最高統治者\NI am the sovereign ruler of the nation of Wakanda.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:34.75,2:05:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我們有史以來第一次\NAnd for the first time in our history...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:37.69,2:05:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,與外界分享交流\Nwe will be sharing our knowledge and resources...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:40.99,2:05:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的知識和資源\Nwith the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:43.03,2:05:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦坎達不再會置身於幕後\NWakanda will no longer watch from the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:46.67,2:05:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不能\NWe cannot.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:49.30,2:05:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也不應該\NWe must not.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:50.97,2:05:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我們將努力成為一個榜樣\NWe will work to be an example of how we...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:53.81,2:05:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,向世人展示 如何像對待兄弟姐妹一樣\Nas brothers and sisters on this earth...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:56.34,2:05:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,對待地球上的同胞\Nshould treat each other.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:58.51,2:06:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,今昔不比往日\NNow, more than ever...
Dialogue: 0,2:06:01.38,2:06:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,分裂的假象威脅著我們的存在\Nthe illusions of division threaten our very existence.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:06.45,2:06:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我們都知道真相\NWe all know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:08.32,2:06:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的共同點遠大於我們的分歧點\NMore connects us than separates us.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:11.99,2:06:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但是在危機時刻\NBut in times of crisis...
Dialogue: 0,2:06:13.89,2:06:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,智者將建立橋樑\Nthe wise build bridges...
Dialogue: 0,2:06:16.60,2:06:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,而愚者則建立高牆\Nwhile the foolish build barriers.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:19.57,2:06:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我們必須達成共識\NWe must find a way...
Dialogue: 0,2:06:21.74,2:06:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,同舟共濟\Nto look after one another...
Dialogue: 0,2:06:24.57,2:06:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,構建人類命運共同體\Nas if we were one, single tribe.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:29.28,2:06:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,恕我直言 國王特查拉\NWith all due respect, King T'Challa...
Dialogue: 0,2:06:30.98,2:06:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你們一個農耕國家\Nwhat can a nation of farmers
Dialogue: 0,2:06:32.25,2:06:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,能向全世界貢獻什麼呢？\Nhave to offer the rest of the world?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:33.71,2:13:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你們又在那個人的旁邊胡鬧吧\NAre you playing around with that man again?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:35.79,2:13:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 沒有 - 你又在逗他了\N- No. - You're teasing him again.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:38.21,2:13:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- 別吵醒他 他需要休息 - 我沒有\N- Don't wake him. He must rest. - No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:41.30,2:13:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有\NNo, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:43.64,2:13:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,塔博 就是你幹的\NThabo, you're doing that.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:45.01,2:13:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是他幹的 他撒謊\NHe's doing it. He's lying.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:46.56,2:13:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不要鬧了 他在休息呢\NNo, he's resting.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:48.27,2:13:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,去玩吧\NGo, go!
Dialogue: 0,2:13:49.64,2:13:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,白狼\NWhite Wolf!
Dialogue: 0,2:13:51.56,2:13:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,別鬧了\NStop that!
Dialogue: 0,2:13:52.73,2:13:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,白狼\NWhite Wolf!
Dialogue: 0,2:13:56.61,2:13:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 巴恩斯中士\NGood morning, Sergeant Barnes.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:59.74,2:14:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我巴基就行\NBucky.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:02.36,2:14:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你感覺如何\NHow are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:04.03,2:14:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好的\NGood.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:07.66,2:14:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:08.83,2:14:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我來\NCome.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:11.87,2:14:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你要學的東西還有很多\NMuch more for you to learn.


